{"data":[{"date":"19:47 21/08","title":"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin t\u1ed1i 21/8: H\u00e0 \u0110\u1ee9c Chinh ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau c\u1ee7a Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/21/diem-tin-toi-218-ha-duc-chinh-tiet-lo-muc-tieu-cua-olympic-viet-nam.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>H\u00e0 \u0110\u1ee9c Chinh ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau c\u1ee7a Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam, Mourinho b\u1ecb nh\u1eadn x\u00e9t gi\u1ed1ng Wenger,... l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt trong m\u1ee5c \u0111i\u1ec3m tin t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y 21/8.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 t\u1eeb HLV Arsene Wenger, Thierry Henry \u0111ang mu\u1ed1n t\u1edbi d\u1eabn d\u1eaft Bourdeaux. Henry t\u1eebng g\u00e2y \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng khi g\u00f3p c\u00f4ng gi\u00fap \u0110T B\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ee9ng th\u1ee9 ba chung cu\u1ed9c t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018 trong vai tr\u00f2 tr\u1ee3 l\u00fd HLV.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin t\u1ed1i 218 H\u00e0 \u0110\u1ee9c Chinh ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin t\u1ed1i 218 H\u00e0 \u0110\u1ee9c Chinh ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/21/duc-chinh-1.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>H\u00e0 \u0110\u1ee9c Chinh ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau c\u1ee7a Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam l\u00e0 ti\u1ebfn v\u00e0o chung k\u1ebft.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTr\u01b0\u1edbc cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1edbi Bahrain t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng 16 \u0111\u1ed9i, H\u00e0 \u0110\u1ee9c Chinh ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau c\u1ee7a Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam t\u1ea1i ASIAD 2018 l\u00e0 ti\u1ebfn t\u1edbi tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Gabriel Jesus t\u1ef1 tin s\u1ebd ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1 c\u1eb7p v\u1edbi Sergio Aguero tr\u00ean h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng. M\u00f9a n\u00e0y, ch\u00e2n s\u00fat tr\u1ebb ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p m\u1ed9t b\u00e0n cho Man City t\u1ea1i Premier League.&nbsp;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ph\u00f3ng vi\u00ean Farabi Firdausy c\u1ee7a Indonesia nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Quang H\u1ea3i l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd b\u1eadc nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam t\u1ea1i ASIAD 2018. T\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u n\u0103m nay, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 g\u1ed1c \u0110\u00f4ng Anh \u0111\u00e3 ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 2 b\u00e0n \u0111\u1ec1u t\u1eeb nh\u1eefng c\u00fa \u0111\u1ec7m l\u00f2ng hi\u1ec3m h\u00f3c.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Roberto Firmino \u0111ang h\u01b0\u1edbng \u0111\u1ebfn vi\u1ec7c ph\u00e1 k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil ghi nhi\u1ec1u b\u00e0n th\u1eafng nh\u1ea5t t\u1ea1i Premier League c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i c\u0169 Philippe Coutinho. Hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, Firmino \u0111\u00e3 ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 36 b\u00e0n, k\u00e9m Coutinho 5 b\u00e0n.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo gi\u1edbi truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng Anh ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9, Chelsea \u0111ang d\u1ef1 t\u00ednh gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Eden Hazard nh\u1eb1m gi\u1eef ch\u00e2n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y kh\u1ecfi s\u1ef1 ve v\u00e3n c\u1ee7a Real Madrid. \u0110i\u1ec1u \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 m\u1ee9c l\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1ee7a Hazard s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u0103ng l\u00ean con s\u1ed1 300.000 b\u1ea3ng m\u1ed7i tu\u1ea7n.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u1ec3 thua \u0111\u1eadm n\u1eef Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n v\u1edbi t\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 0-7, HLV Mai \u0110\u1ee9c Chung kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ki\u1ec1m ch\u1ebf \u0111\u00e3 to ti\u1ebfng v\u1edbi c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u1eef Vi\u1ec7t Nam ngay tr\u00ean s\u00e2n trong gi\u1edd ngh\u1ec9 gi\u1eefa hai hi\u1ec7p. D\u00f9 th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i nh\u01b0ng \u0110T n\u1eef Vi\u1ec7t Nam v\u1eabn l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft v\u00e0 s\u1ebd g\u1eb7p \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u1ea5t b\u1ea3ng A.&nbsp;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Mourinho\" title=\"Mourinho\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/21/mu-phan-ung-ra-sao-sau-tin-don-sa-thai-mourinho-bo-nhiem-zidane.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Jose Mourinho \u0111ang trong t\u00ecnh c\u1ea3nh kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n t\u1ea1i Man Utd.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u1ef1u danh th\u1ee7 Arsenal, Ian Wright nh\u1eadn x\u00e9t Jose Mourinho \u0111ang c\u00f3 chung ho\u00e0n c\u1ea3nh v\u1edbi Arsene Wenger trong nh\u1eefng n\u0103m cu\u1ed1i, khi c\u1ea3 hai \u0111\u1ec1u m\u1ea5t l\u00f2ng tin nghi\u00eam tr\u1ecdng t\u1eeb c\u00e1c c\u1ed5 \u0111\u1ed9ng vi\u00ean.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo \u0111\u1ecbnh gi\u00e1 t\u1eeb Transfermarkt, Olympic Th\u00e1i Lan t\u1ea1i ASIAD 2018 c\u00f3 gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb cao g\u1ea5p 16 l\u1ea7n so v\u1edbi Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam (2.03 tri\u1ec7u so v\u1edbi 125.000 euro). D\u00f9 v\u1eady, Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam gi\u00e0nh quy\u1ec1n v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng 16 \u0111\u1ed9i trong khi Th\u00e1i Lan b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i t\u1eeb v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Vincent Kompany kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh t\u1eadp th\u1ec3 Man City kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 t\u1ef1 m\u00e3n sau ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Premier League 2017-18. Trung v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 cho r\u1eb1ng \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 c\u01a1 s\u1edf \u0111\u1ec3 Man City l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean sau 10 n\u0103m b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng ng\u00f4i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Premier League.<br>\r\n<h2>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt kh\u00e1c tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn ng\u00e0y 21/8:</h2>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/nguoi-dai-dien-cua-pogba-chi-trich-huyen-thoai-mu-172-195008.html\">Ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a Pogba ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i M.U</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/man-city-sap-mua-duoc-gavin-bazunu-172-195006.html\">Man City chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n tu\u1ed5i teen</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/marc-cucurella-muon-roi-barca-180-195005.html\">T\u00e0i n\u0103ng tr\u1ebb Barca quy\u1ebft d\u1ee9t \u00e1o ra \u0111i</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/chuyen-nhuong-real-madrid-hot-nhat-ngay-2108-180-195004.html\">Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Real Madrid hot nh\u1ea5t ng\u00e0y 21/08</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/bao-han-quoc-len-tieng-canh-bao-olympic-viet-nam-truoc-tran-gap-bahrain-168-195003.html\">B\u00e1o H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng c\u1ea3nh b\u00e1o Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Bahrain</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/5-dieu-rut-ra-sau-tran-dau-palace-02-liverpool-172-195001.html\">5 \u0111i\u1ec1u r\u00fat ra sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Palace 0-2 Liverpool</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p (TTVN)</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2625","checkdouble":"195009"},{"date":"19:55 21/08","title":"B\u1ecb gi\u1edbi chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch sau tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n, HLV Park Hang Seo n\u00f3i g\u00ec?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/19/bi-gioi-chuyen-mon-chi-trich-sau-tran-gap-nhat-ban-hlv-park-hang-seo-noi-gi.JPG","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Chia s\u1ebb sau bu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n chi\u1ec1u 21/8, HLV Park Hang Seo \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 c\u00e2u tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng nh\u00e2n s\u1ef1 \u1edf tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n.\r\n\r\n\r\n</h2><br>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111\u1ea5u cu\u1ed1i v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng ASIAD 2018, \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 1-0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n. M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 v\u1eady h\u1ecd ph\u1ea3i tr\u1ea3 c\u00e1i gi\u00e1 kh\u00e1 \u0111\u1eaft khi H\u00f9ng D\u0169ng b\u1ecb g\u00e3y ng\u00f3n ch\u00e2n v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c thi \u0111\u1ea5u, trong khi Quang H\u1ea3i c\u0169ng g\u1eb7p ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng nh\u1eb9.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u1eefng \u00fd ki\u1ebfn cho r\u1eb1ng kh\u00f4ng n\u00ean s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh v\u1edbi nhi\u1ec1u g\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1eb7t ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng nh\u1ea5t tr\u01b0\u1edbc ng\u01b0\u1eddi Nh\u1eadt, HLV Park Hang Seo \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 c\u00e2u tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"B\u1ecb gi\u1edbi chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch, HLV Park Hang Seo n\u00f3i g\u00ec h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"B\u1ecb gi\u1edbi chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch, HLV Park Hang Seo n\u00f3i g\u00ec h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/19/hlv-park-hang-seo-tiet-lo-bi-quyet-thanh-cong-cung-dt-olympic-viet-nam.JPG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>HLV&nbsp;Park Hang Seo ph\u1ea3n b\u00e1c nh\u1eefng ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch c\u1ee7a gi\u1edbi chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c chia s\u1ebb: &ldquo;&ldquo;Gi\u1edbi chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ph\u00e2n t\u00edch v\u00e0 ph\u00ea ph\u00e1n chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Olympic Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n. V\u00ec sau tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng Olympic Nepal, ch\u00fang ta \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng sau. Nh\u01b0ng t\u00f4i ngh\u0129 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u v\u1ec1 c\u00e1ch ti\u1ebfp c\u1eadn v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n v\u00ec ch\u00fang ta ch\u01b0a x\u00e1c \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 ti\u1ebfp theo<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf sau tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng Nepal, t\u00f4i c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 suy ngh\u0129 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n. Ch\u00fang ta c\u00f3 s\u1ed1 ng\u00e0y ngh\u1ec9 tr\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0 sau tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Olympic Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n \u0111\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec3 h\u1ed3i ph\u1ee5c th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c. T\u1ed1n s\u1ee9c th\u00ec tr\u1eadn n\u00e0o c\u0169ng t\u1ed1n s\u1ee9c th\u00f4i. Ng\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ea1i, t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n thay \u0111\u1ed5i nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u00fang ta nh\u1eadn tr\u1eadn thua tan t\u00e1c r\u1ed3i, khi\u1ebfn ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 phi\u1ec1n l\u00f2ng&rdquo;. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">HLV Park Hang Seo c\u0169ng t\u1ecf ra ti\u1ebfc nu\u1ed1i khi ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 H\u00f9ng D\u0169ng d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng. Theo \u00f4ng, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t t\u1ed5n th\u1ea5t n\u1eb7ng n\u1ec1 m\u00e0 m\u00ecnh kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 mu\u1ed1nsong kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh trong b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1, r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec3 bi\u1ebft c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0o c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 g\u1eb7p ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng khi thi \u0111\u1ea5u.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u1ecfi v\u1ec1 \u0111i\u1ec3m y\u1ebfu, \u00f4ng Park t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i kh\u00e9o: &ldquo;T\u00f4i xin gi\u1eef b\u00ed m\u1eadt v\u1ec1 \u0111i\u1ec3m y\u1ebfu c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u. T\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean, Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111ang ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 ngh\u0129a ho\u00e0n h\u1ea3o&rdquo;.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n ng\u01b0\u1eddi H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c c\u0169ng cho bi\u1ebft \u0111\u1ed9i s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c nghi\u00ean c\u1ee9u Bahrain \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u ng\u00e0y 23/8 t\u1edbi.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/diem-tin-toi-218-ha-duc-chinh-tiet-lo-muc-tieu-cua-olympic-viet-nam-184-195009.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/21/diem-tin-toi-218-ha-duc-chinh-tiet-lo-muc-tieu-cua-olympic-viet-nam.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/diem-tin-toi-218-ha-duc-chinh-tiet-lo-muc-tieu-cua-olympic-viet-nam-184-195009.html\">\u0110i\u1ec3m tin t\u1ed1i 21/8: H\u00e0 \u0110\u1ee9c Chinh ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau c\u1ee7a Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam</span><br>\r\nH\u00e0 \u0110\u1ee9c Chinh ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau c\u1ee7a Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam, Mourinho b\u1ecb nh\u1eadn x\u00e9t gi\u1ed1ng Wenger,... l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt trong m\u1ee5c \u0111i\u1ec3m tin t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y 21/8.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/bao-han-quoc-len-tieng-canh-bao-olympic-viet-nam-truoc-tran-gap-bahrain-168-195003.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/19/bao-han-quoc-len-tieng-canh-bao-olympic-viet-nam-truoc-tran-gap-bahrain.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/bao-han-quoc-len-tieng-canh-bao-olympic-viet-nam-truoc-tran-gap-bahrain-168-195003.html\">B\u00e1o H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng c\u1ea3nh b\u00e1o Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Bahrain</span><br>\r\nM\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y t\u1edd Chosun (H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c) \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng c\u1ea3nh b\u00e1o \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ph\u00e9p thi \u0111\u1ea5u ch\u1ee7 quan tr\u01b0\u1edbc Bahrain.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/nguoi-thai-phan-ung-the-nao-sau-man-trinh-dien-te-hai-cua-doi-nha-o-asiad-168-195000.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/21/nguoi-thai-phan-ung-the-nao-sau-man-trinh-dien-te-hai-cua-doi-nha-o-asiad.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/nguoi-thai-phan-ung-the-nao-sau-man-trinh-dien-te-hai-cua-doi-nha-o-asiad-168-195000.html\">Ng\u01b0\u1eddi Th\u00e1i ph\u1ea3n \u1ee9ng th\u1ebf n\u00e0o sau m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n t\u1ec7 h\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0 \u1edf ASIAD?</span><br>\r\nGi\u1edbi truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ea5t n\u01b0\u1edbc Ch\u00f9a v\u00e0ng \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ecf ra c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng v\u1edbi m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n c\u1ee7a \u0110T Olympic Th\u00e1i Lan t\u1ea1i ASIAD v\u1eeba qua, trong khi L\u0110B\u0110 Th\u00e1i Lan l\u1ea1i c\u00f3 suy...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/nhin-lai-nhung-tran-thua-cua-bong-da-bahrain-truoc-viet-nam-168-194992.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2016/10/26/Khep-lai-VCK-U19-chau-A-2016-Buoc-ngoat-lich-su-hinh-anh-2.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/nhin-lai-nhung-tran-thua-cua-bong-da-bahrain-truoc-viet-nam-168-194992.html\">Nh\u00ecn l\u1ea1i nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn thua c\u1ee7a b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Bahrain tr\u01b0\u1edbc Vi\u1ec7t Nam</span><br>\r\nTrong qu\u00e1 kh\u1ee9, c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng \u00edt l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Bahrain. V\u00e0 t\u1ef7 l\u1ec7 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u0111ang nghi\u00eang h\u1eb3n v\u1ec1 ph\u00eda Vi\u1ec7t Nam.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)<span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;&#10;line-height:115%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2624","checkdouble":"195010"},{"date":"20:10 21/08","title":"Th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n B\u00f9i Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng l\u1eadp k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c ch\u01b0a t\u1eebng c\u00f3 t\u1ea1i ASIAD 2018","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/21/thu-mon-bui-tien-dung-lap-ky-luc-tai-asiad-2018.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Nh\u1eefng tranh c\u00e3i ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e0o s\u00e2u khi c\u1ef1u danh th\u1ee7 Man Utd, Lee Sharpe ch\u00ea Paul Pogba th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n phong \u0111\u1ed9 k\u00e9m \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh, l\u00e0 nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n d\u1eabn t\u1edbi phong \u0111\u1ed9 tr\u1ed3i s\u1ee5t c\u1ee7a \"qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf\".</h2><h2>C\u1ef1u danh th\u1ee7 Man Utd ch\u00ea Paul Pogba<br>\r\n\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau khi Paul Scholes l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Man Utd thi\u1ebfu m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng d\u1eabn d\u1eaft to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i ti\u1ebfn l\u00ean, \u0111\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3t m\u1ed9t c\u1ef1u \"qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf\" kh\u00e1c l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng. Lee Sharpe b\u00eanh v\u1ef1c \u00fd ki\u1ebfn c\u1ee7a Scholes khi cho r\u1eb1ng Pogba thi \u0111\u1ea5u ch\u01b0a \u0111\u1ee7 t\u1ed1t trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Man Utd.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"C\u1ef1u danh th\u1ee7 Man Utd ch\u00ea Paul Pogba h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"C\u1ef1u danh th\u1ee7 Man Utd ch\u00ea Paul Pogba h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/21/Cuu-danh-thu-Man-Utd-che-Paul-Pogba-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>C\u1ef1u danh th\u1ee7 Man Utd ch\u00ea Paul Pogba kh\u00f4ng gi\u1eef \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c phong \u0111\u1ed9 \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\"Anh \u1ea5y ch\u01b0a \u0111\u1ee7 ti\u00eau chu\u1ea9n\" - C\u1ef1u danh th\u1ee7 Man Utd ch\u00ea Paul Pogba: \"Ch\u00fang ta \u0111\u1ec1u th\u1ea5y ti\u00eau chu\u1ea9n c\u1ee7a anh \u1ea5y trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o \u0110T Ph\u00e1p, ch\u00e0ng trai cao l\u1edbn n\u00e0y c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0m m\u1ecdi \u0111i\u1ec1u nh\u01b0ng l\u1ea1i kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c phong \u0111\u1ed9 \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u1eb7n trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o \u0111\u1ecf\".<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\"Ch\u00fang ta kh\u00f4ng bi\u1ebft \u0111i\u1ec1u g\u00ec \u0111\u00e3 x\u1ea3y ra trong ph\u00f2ng thay \u0111\u1ed3, kh\u00f4ng bi\u1ebft anh \u1ea5t n\u00f3i g\u00ec v\u00e0 ch\u1ec9 d\u1eabn t\u1eeb hu\u1ea5n luy\u1ec7n vi\u00ean. Nh\u01b0ng ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn anh \u1ea5y ch\u01b0a tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n \u0111\u00fang kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng. L\u1ebd ra, Pogba ph\u1ea3i ch\u1ee9ng minh anh \u1ea5y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 hay nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi trong m\u1ecdi tu\u1ea7n. Nh\u01b0ng v\u00ec m\u1ed9t v\u00e0i l\u00fd do, Pogba kh\u00f4ng l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3\".\u00a0<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Nh\u1eefng tranh c\u00e3i v\u1ec1 Pogba<br>\r\n\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau tr\u1eadn thua s\u1ed1c c\u1ee7a Man Utd v\u1edbi Brighton (2-3) t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng 2 Premier League 2018-19, Scholes \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1eb7t ra c\u00e2u h\u1ecfi v\u1ec1 s\u1ef1 c\u1ed1ng hi\u1ebfn c\u1ee7a Pogba. Kh\u00f4ng l\u00e2u sau, Mino Raiola - ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a Pogba - \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch Scholes.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Gi\u1edbi truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng Anh c\u0169ng \u0111\u0103ng t\u1ea3i nh\u1eefng th\u00f4ng tin v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c Paul Pogba \u0111\u00f2i ra \u0111i trong k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00e8 2018. M\u1ed9t b\u1ed9 ph\u1eadn kh\u00e1c c\u0169ng kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u00e2y ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 chi\u00eau tr\u00f2 c\u1ee7a Mino Raiola nh\u1eb1m \u0111\u00f2i ban l\u00e3nh \u0111\u1ea1o Man Utd t\u0103ng l\u01b0\u01a1ng cho Pogba.<br>\r\n<h2>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft kh\u00e1c tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn v\u1ec1 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Paul Pogba:</h2>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/nguoi-dai-dien-cua-pogba-chi-trich-huyen-thoai-mu-172-195008.html\">Ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a Pogba ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i M.U</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/sieu-co-raiola-chi-trich-scholes-san-sang-dem-pogba-roi-mu-172-194987.html\">Si\u00eau c\u00f2 Raiola ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch Scholes, s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng \u0111em Pogba r\u1eddi M.U</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/diem-tin-bong-da-sang-ngay-218-barca-dinh-ngay-don-pogba-184-194949.html\">\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 s\u00e1ng ng\u00e0y 21/8: Barca \u0111\u1ecbnh ng\u00e0y \u0111\u00f3n Pogba</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/scholes-chi-trich-pogba-sau-tran-thua-brighton-172-194879.html\">Scholes \u0111\u1eb7t d\u1ea5u h\u1ecfi v\u1ec1 l\u1eddi nh\u1eadn l\u1ed7i c\u1ee7a Pogba</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/pogba-len-tieng-xin-loi-sau-tran-thua-bac-nhuoc-cua-mu-172-194851.html\">Pogba l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng xin l\u1ed7i sau tr\u1eadn thua b\u1ea1c nh\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ee7a M.U</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/pogba-va-mourinho-can-phai-truong-thanh-hon-172-194812.html\">Pogba v\u00e0 Mourinho c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i tr\u01b0\u1edfng th\u00e0nh h\u01a1n</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>N.D (TTVN)</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2623","checkdouble":"195011"},{"date":"20:26 21/08","title":"N\u00f3ng: Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh FC s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng b\u1ecf V-League v\u00ec l\u00fd do b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/4/14/nong-nam-dinh-san-sang-bo-vleague-vi-ly-do-bat-ngo.JPG","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea3m nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 t\u1eeb l\u00e3nh \u0111\u1ea1o t\u1ec9nh, HLV Nguy\u1ec5n V\u0103n S\u1ef9 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng b\u1ecf V-League \u0111\u1ec3 quay tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 gi\u1ea3i h\u1ea1ng nh\u1ea5t.</h2><h2>Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng b\u1ecf V-League<br />\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong cu\u1ed9c ph\u1ecfng v\u1ea5n tr\u00ean OnSports, HLV Nguy\u1ec5n V\u0103n S\u1ef9 g\u00e2y s\u1ed1c v\u1edbi chia s\u1ebb \u0111\u1ea7y b\u1ee9c x\u00fac r\u1eb1ng d\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u01b0 l\u00e3nh \u0111\u1ea1o t\u1ec9nh kh\u00f4ng quan t\u00e2m \u0111\u1ebfn Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh FC: &quot;Th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 t\u00f4i r\u1ea5t bu\u1ed3n khi nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u00f3 tr\u00e1ch nhi\u1ec7m kh\u00f4ng quan t\u00e2m&quot;.&nbsp;<br />\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"N\u00f3ng Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng b\u1ecf V-League v\u00ec l\u00fd do b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"N\u00f3ng Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng b\u1ecf V-League v\u00ec l\u00fd do b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/14/nong-nam-dinh-san-sang-bo-vleague-vi-ly-do-bat-ngo.JPG\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>HLV Nguy\u1ec5n V\u0103n S\u1ef9 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng b\u1ecf V-League \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 gi\u1ea3i h\u1ea1ng nh\u1ea5t.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br />\r\n&quot;Th\u1eadm ch\u00ed, t\u00f4i c\u00f3 c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c nh\u01b0 ki\u1ec3u mu\u1ed1n cho \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng quay tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 gi\u1ea3i h\u1ea1ng nh\u1ea5t. N\u1ebfu th\u1ea3 h\u1eb3n nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf th\u00ec c\u1ee9 n\u00f3i m\u1ed9t c\u00e2u l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng nu\u00f4i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd d\u1eebng l\u1ea1i&quot;.<br />\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau b\u1ea3y n\u0103m v\u1eafng b\u00f3ng, Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh FC m\u1edbi tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i s\u00e2n ch\u01a1i V-League \u1edf m\u00f9a n\u00e0y. Tuy nhi\u00ean, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Nam thi \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00e1 th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng khi m\u1edbi gi\u00e0nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 18 \u0111i\u1ec3m sau 20 v\u00f2ng, \u0111\u1ee9ng \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed \u00e1p ch\u00f3t khi ch\u1ec9 h\u01a1n XSKT C\u1ea7n Th\u01a1 \u0111\u00fang 1 \u0111i\u1ec3m.<br />\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>V\u00ec \u0111\u00e2u n\u00ean n\u1ed7i<br />\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n khi\u1ebfn Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh FC ch\u01a1i kh\u00f4ng t\u1ed1t t\u1ea1i V-League 2018 m\u1ed9t ph\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1eeb vi\u1ec7c c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u01b0a quen v\u1edbi nh\u1ecbp \u0111\u1ed9 thi \u0111\u1ea5u nh\u01b0 ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3 t\u1eeb HLV Nguy\u1ec5n V\u0103n S\u1ef9. H\u01a1n n\u1eefa, ngo\u1ea1i binh c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Nam c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao.<br />\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tuy nhi\u00ean m\u1ed9t l\u00fd do kh\u00e1c l\u00e0 Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh FC \u0111ang thi\u1ebfu kinh ph\u00ed ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng. Hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh v\u1eabn s\u1ed1ng nh\u1edd b\u1ea7u s\u1eefa c\u1ee7a t\u1ec9nh n\u00ean kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 ngu\u1ed3n l\u1ef1c t\u00e0i ch\u00ednh d\u1ed3i d\u00e0o \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea1nh tranh v\u1edbi c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u1edf V-League. N\u1ebfu t\u00ecnh h\u00ecnh kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 g\u00ec thay \u0111\u1ed5i, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Nam ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 nguy c\u01a1 ph\u1ea3i tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i h\u1ea1ng nh\u1ea5t m\u00f9a t\u1edbi.<br />\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede v\u00f2ng 21 V-League 2018, Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh s\u1ebd ch\u1ea1m tr\u00e1n Sanna Kh\u00e1nh H\u00f2a tr\u00ean s\u00e2n Thi\u00ean Tr\u01b0\u1eddng.<br />\r\n<h2>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft kh\u00e1c tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn v\u1ec1 Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh FC t\u1ea1i V-League 2018:</h2>\r\n<br />\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/danh-roi-chien-thang-truoc-clb-ha-noi-hlv-nam-dinh-noi-gi-168-191331.html\">\u0110\u00e1nh r\u01a1i chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc CLB H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i, HLV Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh n\u00f3i g\u00ec?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/vleague/cdv-nam-dinh-doi-mua-dot-phao-ngay-tai-hang-day-291-191271.html\">C\u0110V Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh \u0111\u1ed9i m\u01b0a \u0111\u1ed1t ph\u00e1o s\u00e1ng ngay t\u1ea1i H\u00e0ng \u0110\u1eaby</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/truc-tiep-bong-da/tran-dau/ha-noi-vs-nam-dinh-vong-19-vleague-2018-372-191252.html\">H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i 3-3 Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh (KT): D\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc 3-0, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Nam v\u1eabn kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 c\u00f3 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/clb-nam-dinh-chinh-thuc-nhan-an-phat-sau-vu-nao-loan-tren-san-thien-truong-168-190948.html\">CLB Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c nh\u1eadn \u00e1n ph\u1ea1t sau v\u1ee5 n\u00e1o lo\u1ea1n tr\u00ean s\u00e2n Thi\u00ean Tr\u01b0\u1eddng</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/cdv-nam-dinh-dai-nao-san-thien-truong-nguoi-trong-cuoc-noi-gi-168-190610.html\">C\u0110V Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh \u0111\u1ea1i n\u00e1o s\u00e2n Thi\u00ean Tr\u01b0\u1eddng, ng\u01b0\u1eddi trong cu\u1ed9c n\u00f3i g\u00ec?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/de-thua-tuong-moi-cua-sai-gon-hlv-nam-dinh-noi-gi-168-190140.html\">\u0110\u1ec3 thua t\u01b0\u1edbng m\u1edbi c\u1ee7a S\u00e0i G\u00f2n, HLV Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh n\u00f3i g\u00ec?</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>N.D (TTVN)</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2622","checkdouble":"195012"},{"date":"20:18 21/08","title":"ASIAD 2018 s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ph\u00e1t s\u00f3ng tr\u00ean nh\u1eefng k\u00eanh n\u00e0o t\u1ea1i Vi\u1ec7t Nam?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/21/asiad-2018-se-duoc-phat-song-tren-nhung-kenh-nao-tai-viet-nam.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Tr\u00ean truy\u1ec1n h\u00ecnh, kh\u00e1n gi\u1ea3 s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xem tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp v\u00e0 xem l\u1ea1i c\u00e1c tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u hay tr\u00ean k\u00eanh VTC1, VTC3, VTC9 c\u1ee7a \u0110\u00e0i Truy\u1ec1n h\u00ecnh k\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt s\u1ed1 VTC v\u00e0 k\u00eanh VOVTV.</h2><p style=\"text-align: left;\">T\u1eeb ng\u00e0y mai (22/8) kh\u00e1n gi\u1ea3 truy\u1ec1n h\u00ecnh c\u1ea3 n\u01b0\u1edbc s\u1ebd ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xem ASIAD 2018 c\u00f3 b\u1ea3n quy\u1ec1n tr\u00ean c\u00e1c k\u00eanh s\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a \u0110\u00e0i truy\u1ec1n h\u00ecnh k\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt s\u1ed1 VTC tr\u1ef1c thu\u1ed9c \u0110\u00e0i ti\u1ebfng n\u00f3i Vi\u1ec7t Nam VOV. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, tr\u00ean ph\u00e1t thanh, th\u00ednh gi\u1ea3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 nghe t\u01b0\u1eddng thu\u1eadt tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp c\u00e1c tr\u1eadn thi \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c \u0110\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Qu\u1ed1c gia, \u0110\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 nam Olympic v\u00e0 tuy\u1ec3n n\u1eef qu\u1ed1c gia Vi\u1ec7t Nam c\u00f9ng c\u00e1c s\u1ef1 ki\u1ec7n th\u1ec3 thao kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 Asiad 2018 tr\u00ean c\u00e1c k\u00eanh s\u00f3ng ph\u00e1t thanh: VOV1, VOV2, VOV3, VOV Giao th\u00f4ng, VOV S\u1ee9c kh\u1ecfe.\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\" title=\"\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/21/ban-quyen-asiad-2018-1.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\u00a0</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTr\u00ean truy\u1ec1n h\u00ecnh, kh\u00e1n gi\u1ea3 s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xem tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp ASIAD 2018 tr\u00ean k\u00eanh VTC1, VTC3, VTC9 c\u1ee7a \u0110\u00e0i Truy\u1ec1n h\u00ecnh k\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt s\u1ed1 VTC v\u00e0 k\u00eanh VOV TV V\u1eady ng\u01b0\u1eddi xem truy\u1ec1n h\u00ecnh c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 xem \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eefng k\u00eanh n\u00e0y \u1edf nh\u1eefng h\u1ea1 t\u1ea7ng truy\u1ec1n h\u00ecnh  n\u00e0o. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc h\u1ebft to\u00e0n b\u1ed9 c\u00e1c k\u00eanh n\u00e0y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ph\u00e1t trong nh\u00f3m k\u00eanh mi\u1ec5n ph\u00ed c\u1ee7a \u0110\u00e0i VTC tr\u00ean h\u1ea1 t\u1ea7ng  truy\u1ec1n h\u00ecnh mi\u1ec5n ph\u00ed DVB-T2. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nDo \u0111\u00f3, nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ecba b\u00e0n n\u1eb1m trong v\u00f9ng ph\u1ee7 s\u00f3ng truy\u1ec1n  h\u00ecnh s\u1ed1 c\u1ee7a VTC s\u1ebd thu xem \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c mi\u1ec5n ph\u00ed k\u00eanh n\u00e0y. \u0110\u1ec3 thu xem \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ng\u01b0\u1eddi d\u00e2n s\u1eed  d\u1ee5ng tivi c\u00f3 t\u00edch h\u1ee3p DVB-T2, ho\u1eb7c tivi \u0111\u1eddi c\u0169 th\u00ec c\u1ea7n c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ea7u thu truy\u1ec1n h\u00ecnh s\u1ed1  m\u1eb7t \u0111\u1ea5t (DVB-T2 v\u00e0 DVB-T) \u0111\u1ec1u c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 thu xem \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u1edbi ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh  \u0111\u1eb9p ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n mi\u1ec5n ph\u00ed.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nHi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i s\u00f3ng truy\u1ec1n h\u00ecnh s\u1ed1 c\u1ee7a VTC \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ee7 \u1edf c\u00e1c t\u1ec9nh \u0111\u1ed3ng b\u1eb1ng B\u1eafc B\u1ed9, Nam B\u1ed9,  m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 t\u1ec9nh mi\u1ec1n n\u00fai nh\u01b0 Cao B\u1eb1ng, S\u01a1n La, \u1edf T\u00e2y Nguy\u00ean c\u00f3 \u0110\u1eafc L\u1eafc c\u0169ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ph\u1ee7  s\u00f3ng truy\u1ec1n h\u00ecnh s\u1ed1 DVB-T2 \u1edf \u0111\u1ecba b\u00e0n th\u00e0nh ph\u1ed1.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNgo\u00e0i ra tr\u00ean c\u00e1c h\u1ea1 t\u1ea7ng truy\u1ec1n h\u00ecnh tr\u1ea3 ti\u1ec1n, ch\u1ec9 tr\u1eeb K+ l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng ph\u00e1t c\u00e1c k\u00eanh c\u1ee7a VTC c\u00f2n  l\u1ea1i t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 c\u00e1c nh\u00e0 cung c\u1ea5p truy\u1ec1n h\u00ecnh tr\u1ea3 ti\u1ec1n nh\u01b0 VTVcab, SCTV, FPT, Viettel,  MyTV, HTVC, d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 truy\u1ec1n h\u00ecnh s\u1ed1 v\u1ec7 tinh VTC \u0111\u1ec1u c\u00f3 truy\u1ec1n d\u1eabn k\u00eanh VTC3, VTC1 ho\u1eb7c VTC9. Do  \u0111\u00f3, kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c nh\u00e0 cung c\u1ea5p truy\u1ec1n h\u00ecnh tr\u1ea3 ti\u1ec1n (tr\u1eeb  K+) \u0111\u1ec1u c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 xem \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00e1c n\u1ed9i dung ASIAD. Tuy nhi\u00ean ri\u00eang k\u00eanh VOV TV th\u00ec c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t \u1edf \u0111\u1ea7y \u0111\u1ee7 c\u00e1c h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng truy\u1ec1n h\u00ecnh tr\u1ea3 ti\u1ec1n l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t Vi\u1ec7t Nam.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nB\u00ean c\u1ea1nh \u0111\u00f3, VTC c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng c\u1ea5p quy\u1ec1n cho c\u00e1c \u0110\u00e0i ph\u00e1t thanh - Truy\u1ec1n h\u00ecnh trong c\u1ea3 n\u01b0\u1edbc, n\u1ebfu c\u00f3 nhu c\u1ea7u, \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ph\u00e9p ti\u1ebfp ph\u00e1t nguy\u00ean tr\u1ea1ng c\u00e1c ch\u01b0\u01a1ng tr\u00ecnh, c\u00e1c tr\u1eadn thi \u0111\u1ea5u do VOV/VTC ph\u00e1t s\u00f3ng trong khu\u00f4n kh\u1ed5 ASIAD 2018. B\u1ea3n th\u00e2n \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n \u0110\u00e0i truy\u1ec1n h\u00ecnh Vi\u1ec7t Nam (VTV) cho hay \u0111\u00e3 s\u1edbm li\u00ean h\u1ec7 v\u1edbi VTC v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c ti\u1ebfp ph\u00e1t s\u00f3ng nguy\u00ean v\u1eb9n ASIAD 2018 tr\u00ean c\u00e1c k\u00eanh qu\u1ea3ng b\u00e1 c\u1ee7a VTV.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u01b0 v\u1eady, r\u1ea5t c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ASIAD 2018 s\u1ebd xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n tr\u00ean v\u00e0i k\u00eanh qu\u1ea3ng b\u00e1 l\u1edbn c\u1ee7a VTV nh\u01b0 VTV3, \u0111\u1ed3ng ngh\u0129a kh\u00e1n gi\u1ea3 c\u1ea3 n\u01b0\u1edbc s\u1ebd c\u00f3 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u c\u00e1ch \u0111\u1ec3 xem ASIAD 2018 m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch h\u1ee3p ph\u00e1p, c\u00f3 b\u1ea3n quy\u1ec1n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c s\u1edf h\u1eefu b\u1ea3n quy\u1ec1n ASIAD 2018 tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea7y \u0111\u1ee7 h\u1ea1 t\u1ea7ng truy\u1ec1n d\u1eabn s\u1ebd gi\u00fap  ng\u01b0\u1eddi d\u00e2n Vi\u1ec7t Nam kh\u1ecfi ph\u1ea3i l\u00f9ng s\u1ee5c \u0111i t\u00ecm \u0111\u1ecba ch\u1ec9 ph\u00e1t s\u00f3ng \u201cl\u1eadu\u201d \u0111\u1ec3 xem nh\u01b0  10 ng\u00e0y qua.</p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2621","checkdouble":"195013"},{"date":"22:45 21/08","title":"\"Kh\u00f4ng hi\u1ec3u sao Paul Pogba ch\u01b0a \u0111\u00e1 \u0111\u00fang s\u1ee9c trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Man Utd\"","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/20/cuu-danh-thu-man-utd-che-paul-pogba.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Nh\u1eefng tranh c\u00e3i ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e0o s\u00e2u khi c\u1ef1u danh th\u1ee7 Man Utd, Lee Sharpe ch\u00ea Paul Pogba th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n phong \u0111\u1ed9 k\u00e9m \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh, l\u00e0 nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n d\u1eabn t\u1edbi phong \u0111\u1ed9 tr\u1ed3i s\u1ee5t c\u1ee7a \"qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf\".</h2><h2>C\u1ef1u danh th\u1ee7 Man Utd ch\u00ea Paul Pogba<br>\r\n\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau khi Paul Scholes l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Man Utd thi\u1ebfu m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng d\u1eabn d\u1eaft to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i ti\u1ebfn l\u00ean, \u0111\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3t m\u1ed9t c\u1ef1u \"qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf\" kh\u00e1c l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng. Lee Sharpe b\u00eanh v\u1ef1c \u00fd ki\u1ebfn c\u1ee7a Scholes khi cho r\u1eb1ng Pogba thi \u0111\u1ea5u ch\u01b0a \u0111\u1ee7 t\u1ed1t trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Man Utd.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"C\u1ef1u danh th\u1ee7 Man Utd ch\u00ea Paul Pogba h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"C\u1ef1u danh th\u1ee7 Man Utd ch\u00ea Paul Pogba h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/21/Cuu-danh-thu-Man-Utd-che-Paul-Pogba-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>C\u1ef1u danh th\u1ee7 Man Utd ch\u00ea Paul Pogba kh\u00f4ng gi\u1eef \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c phong \u0111\u1ed9 \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\"Anh \u1ea5y ch\u01b0a \u0111\u1ee7 ti\u00eau chu\u1ea9n\" - C\u1ef1u danh th\u1ee7 Man Utd ch\u00ea Paul Pogba: \"Ch\u00fang ta \u0111\u1ec1u th\u1ea5y ti\u00eau chu\u1ea9n c\u1ee7a anh \u1ea5y trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o \u0110T Ph\u00e1p, ch\u00e0ng trai cao l\u1edbn n\u00e0y c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0m m\u1ecdi \u0111i\u1ec1u nh\u01b0ng l\u1ea1i kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c phong \u0111\u1ed9 \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u1eb7n trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o \u0111\u1ecf\".<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\"Ch\u00fang ta kh\u00f4ng bi\u1ebft \u0111i\u1ec1u g\u00ec \u0111\u00e3 x\u1ea3y ra trong ph\u00f2ng thay \u0111\u1ed3, kh\u00f4ng bi\u1ebft anh \u1ea5t n\u00f3i g\u00ec v\u00e0 ch\u1ec9 d\u1eabn t\u1eeb hu\u1ea5n luy\u1ec7n vi\u00ean. Nh\u01b0ng ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn anh \u1ea5y ch\u01b0a tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n \u0111\u00fang kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng. L\u1ebd ra, Pogba ph\u1ea3i ch\u1ee9ng minh anh \u1ea5y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 hay nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi trong m\u1ecdi tu\u1ea7n. Nh\u01b0ng v\u00ec m\u1ed9t v\u00e0i l\u00fd do, Pogba kh\u00f4ng l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3\".\u00a0<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Nh\u1eefng tranh c\u00e3i v\u1ec1 Pogba<br>\r\n\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau tr\u1eadn thua s\u1ed1c c\u1ee7a Man Utd v\u1edbi Brighton (2-3) t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng 2 Premier League 2018-19, Scholes \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1eb7t ra c\u00e2u h\u1ecfi v\u1ec1 s\u1ef1 c\u1ed1ng hi\u1ebfn c\u1ee7a Pogba. Kh\u00f4ng l\u00e2u sau, Mino Raiola - ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a Pogba - \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch Scholes.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Gi\u1edbi truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng Anh c\u0169ng \u0111\u0103ng t\u1ea3i nh\u1eefng th\u00f4ng tin v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c Paul Pogba \u0111\u00f2i ra \u0111i trong k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00e8 2018. M\u1ed9t b\u1ed9 ph\u1eadn kh\u00e1c c\u0169ng kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u00e2y ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 chi\u00eau tr\u00f2 c\u1ee7a Mino Raiola nh\u1eb1m \u0111\u00f2i ban l\u00e3nh \u0111\u1ea1o Man Utd t\u0103ng l\u01b0\u01a1ng cho Pogba.<br>\r\n<h2>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft kh\u00e1c tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn v\u1ec1 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Paul Pogba:</h2>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/nguoi-dai-dien-cua-pogba-chi-trich-huyen-thoai-mu-172-195008.html\">Ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a Pogba ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i M.U</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/sieu-co-raiola-chi-trich-scholes-san-sang-dem-pogba-roi-mu-172-194987.html\">Si\u00eau c\u00f2 Raiola ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch Scholes, s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng \u0111em Pogba r\u1eddi M.U</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/diem-tin-bong-da-sang-ngay-218-barca-dinh-ngay-don-pogba-184-194949.html\">\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 s\u00e1ng ng\u00e0y 21/8: Barca \u0111\u1ecbnh ng\u00e0y \u0111\u00f3n Pogba</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/scholes-chi-trich-pogba-sau-tran-thua-brighton-172-194879.html\">Scholes \u0111\u1eb7t d\u1ea5u h\u1ecfi v\u1ec1 l\u1eddi nh\u1eadn l\u1ed7i c\u1ee7a Pogba</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/pogba-len-tieng-xin-loi-sau-tran-thua-bac-nhuoc-cua-mu-172-194851.html\">Pogba l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng xin l\u1ed7i sau tr\u1eadn thua b\u1ea1c nh\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ee7a M.U</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/pogba-va-mourinho-can-phai-truong-thanh-hon-172-194812.html\">Pogba v\u00e0 Mourinho c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i tr\u01b0\u1edfng th\u00e0nh h\u01a1n</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>N.D (TTVN)</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2620","checkdouble":"195014"},{"date":"00:17 22/08","title":"Real Madrid l\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed1i x\u1eed ph\u0169 v\u1edbi th\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ed3ng b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Na Uy","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/21/real-madrid-cho-muon-martin-odergaard.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Th\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u1ee7a b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Na Uy, Martin Odegaard ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c b\u1ecb \u0111\u1ea9y kh\u1ecfi Real Madrid theo d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n t\u1ea1i H\u00e0 Lan v\u1edbi th\u1eddi h\u1ea1n k\u00e9o d\u00e0i m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i.</h2><h2>Real Madrid cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n Martin Odegaard<br>\r\n\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Martin Odegaard, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ec7nh danh l\u00e0 th\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u1ee7a b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Na Uy t\u1eeb n\u0103m 2014 nh\u01b0ng cho \u0111\u1ebfn nay, Real Madrid m\u1edbi \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y ra s\u00e2n hai l\u1ea7n. Odegaard hai m\u00f9a g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t b\u1ecb \u0111\u1ea9y sang Heerenveen theo d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Real Madrid cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n Martin Odegaard h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Real Madrid cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n Martin Odegaard h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/21/real-madrid-cho-muon-martin-odergaard.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Real Madrid cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n Martin Odergaard th\u00eam m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTrong hai m\u00f9a kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Heerenveen, Odegaard ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 4 b\u00e0n sau 43 tr\u1eadn ra s\u00e2n. M\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n \u0111\u00f3 ch\u01b0a \u0111\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec3 thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c HLV Julen Lopetegui gi\u1eef c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y \u1edf l\u1ea1i Bernabeu \u0111\u1ec3 trao c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i. V\u00ec v\u1eady, Odegaard ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c ph\u1ea3i r\u1eddi Real Madrid \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1edbi Vitesse theo d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Vitesse l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t CLB t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i V\u0110QG H\u00e0 Lan. H\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u1ee7a Odegaard v\u1edbi Vitesse s\u1ebd c\u00f3 th\u1eddi h\u1ea1n \u0111\u1ebfn h\u1ebft 30/6/2019.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Odegaard n\u00f3i g\u00ec?<br>\r\n\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u00e3 c\u00f3 12 tr\u1eadn ra s\u00e2n cho \u0110T Na Uy nh\u01b0ng Odegaard v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Real Madrid trao c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i. Chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c ph\u1ea3i ra \u0111i theo d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n, Odegaard cho bi\u1ebft: \"T\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 kinh nghi\u1ec7m thi \u0111\u1ea5u m\u1ed9t n\u0103m r\u01b0\u1ee1i t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i V\u0110QG H\u00e0 Lan\".<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\"T\u00f4i r\u1ea5t \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1edbi Vitesse. T\u00f4i bi\u1ebft \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng m\u1ea1nh v\u1edbi l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng v\u00e0 ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t th\u1ebf tr\u1eadn. T\u00f4i ngh\u0129 c\u00e1ch ch\u01a1i n\u00e0y ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n. \u0110\u00e2y c\u0169ng l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng lu\u00f4n trao c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i cho c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 l\u00fd do t\u00f4i h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac v\u1edbi c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i m\u00e0 Vitesse trao cho\".<br>\r\n<h2>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft kh\u00e1c tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn v\u1ec1 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Martin Odegaard:</h2>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/3-doi-bong-anh-muon-co-than-dong-cua-real-madrid-180-194418.html\">3 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Anh mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 th\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u1ee7a Real Madrid</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/than-dong-khong-lon-van-dat-niem-tin-vao-real-madrid-180-161707.html\">\u201cTh\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ed3ng kh\u00f4ng l\u1edbn\u201d v\u1eabn \u0111\u1eb7t ni\u1ec1m tin v\u00e0o Real Madrid</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/real-chinh-thuc-chia-tay-ngoi-sao-dau-tien-trong-thang-mot-172-151840.html\">Real ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c chia tay ng\u00f4i sao \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean trong th\u00e1ng M\u1ed9t</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/video/sao-tre-than-dong-real-martin-odegaard-re-bong-hay-dut-diem-toi-328-146942.html\">Th\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ed3ng Real r\u00ea b\u00f3ng t\u1ef1a Messi, d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u01b0 Bendtner</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/rashford-khien-than-dong-real-madrid-phuc-sat-dat-172-142414.html\">Rashford khi\u1ebfn th\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ed3ng Real Madrid ph\u1ee5c s\u00e1t \u0111\u1ea5t</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/nghi-van-zidane-lai-bi-ep-dung-odegaard-o-champions-league-180-142147.html\">Nghi v\u1ea5n: Zidane l\u1ea1i b\u1ecb \u201c\u00e9p\u201d d\u00f9ng Odegaard \u1edf Champions League?</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>N.D (TTVN)</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2619","checkdouble":"195015"},{"date":"06:05 22/08","title":"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 s\u00e1ng 22/8: Zidane thay Mourinho v\u00e0 ti\u1ebfng n\u00f3i c\u1ee7a MU","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/31/diem-tin-bong-da-sang-228-zidane-thay-mourinho-va-tieng-noi-cua-mu.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 \u0111\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c chuy\u00ean trang B\u00f3ng \u0110\u00e1 24h t\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p trong m\u1ee5c \u0111i\u1ec3m tin s\u00e1ng ng\u00e0y 22/8.</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Man Utd ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng v\u1ec1 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Zidane thay Mourinho</h2>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin bongda24hvn s\u00e1ng ng\u00e0y 228 - Tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 24h m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin bongda24hvn s\u00e1ng ng\u00e0y 228 - Tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 24h m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/31/diem-tin-bong-da-toi-158-vi-man-utd-zidane-san-sang-lat-keo-juventus.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>HLV Zinedine Zidane</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u201cT\u1ea1i sao ch\u00fang ta l\u1ea1i ph\u1ea3i \u0111i b\u00e0n lu\u1eadn v\u1ec1 Zidane khi ch\u1eb3ng c\u00f3 th\u1eeba vi\u1ec7c g\u00ec \u1edf \u0111\u00e2y v\u1eady?\u201d \u2013 M\u1ed9t nh\u00e2n v\u1eadt n\u1ed9i b\u1ed9 c\u1ea5p cao \u1edf Old Trafford \u0111\u00e3 chia s\u1ebb tr\u01b0\u1edbc tin \u0111\u1ed3n d\u1ed3n d\u1eadp. Jose Mourinho \u0111ang \u0111\u1ee9ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc nguy c\u01a1 cao b\u1ecb Man Utd sa th\u1ea3i b\u1edfi th\u00e0nh t\u00edch b\u1ebft b\u00e1t tr\u00ean s\u00e2n c\u1ecf c\u00f9ng m\u00e2u thu\u1eabn kh\u00f3 h\u00f2a gi\u1ea3i v\u1edbi c\u1ea3 ban l\u00e3nh \u0111\u1ea1o v\u00e0 c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7. Trong khi \u0111\u00f3, Zinedine Zidane \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng t\u00e1i xu\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 v\u00ec Qu\u1ef7 \u0110\u1ecf, \u00edt l\u00e2u sau khi chia tay Real Madrid tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ec9nh vinh quang.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u00ecnh ti\u1ebft m\u1edbi trong chuy\u1ec7n \u0111i \u1edf c\u1ee7a ng\u00f4i sao Man Utd<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 s\u00e1ng 228 Zidane thay Mourinho v\u00e0 ti\u1ebfng n\u00f3i c\u1ee7a MU h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" title=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 s\u00e1ng 228 Zidane thay Mourinho v\u00e0 ti\u1ebfng n\u00f3i c\u1ee7a MU h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/20/Diem-tin-bong-da-sang-228-Zidane-thay-Mourinho-va-tieng-noi-cua-MU-hinh-anh-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Anthony Martial</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Anthony Martial v\u1ed1n kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u00f2ng Jose Mourinho v\u00ec v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n, v\u00e0 r\u1ed3i nh\u1eefng m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n tr\u00ean s\u00e2n c\u1ecf d\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u01b0 c\u0169ng ch\u1eb3ng gi\u00fap \u00edch \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c g\u00ec nhi\u1ec1u cho ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p. Tuy nhi\u00ean tr\u00e1i ng\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed3n \u0111o\u00e1n tr\u01b0\u1edbc gi\u1edd, Martial th\u1ef1c ra quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m b\u00e1m tr\u1ee5 l\u1ea1i Old Trafford \u0111\u1ec3 chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u cho ch\u1ed7 \u0111\u1ee9ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, trong khi ch\u00ednh Mourinho m\u1edbi y\u00eau c\u1ea7u ban l\u00e3nh \u0111\u1ea1o Qu\u1ef7 \u0110\u1ecf b\u00e1n qu\u00e1ch \u0111i h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 23 tu\u1ed5i.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Barcelona v\u1eabn c\u00f3 quy\u1ec1n \u0111\u00f2i l\u1ea1i Yerry Mina nh\u01b0ng ph\u1ea3i ch\u1edd<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Mina chinh thuc toi Everton\" title=\"Mina ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c t\u1edbi Everton\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/9/yerry-mina-chinh-thuc-cap-ben-ngoai-hang-anh.PNG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Yerry Mina</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 \u0111\u00e3 b\u00e1n \u0111\u1ee9t trung v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Colombia cho Everton v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 27 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng, Barcelona v\u1eabn g\u00e0i th\u00eam v\u00e0o h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111i\u1ec1u kho\u1ea3n mua l\u1ea1i v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 g\u1ea5p \u0111\u00f4i (54 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng \u2013 60 tri\u1ec7u Euro), tuy nhi\u00ean ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u00edch ho\u1ea1t b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u t\u1eeb m\u00f9a h\u00e8 2020. Mina l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong ba c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Barca \u0111\u1ed3ng lo\u1ea1i c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Goodison Park trong k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00e8 2018 n\u00e0y, b\u00ean c\u1ea1nh Lucas Digne v\u00e0 Andre Gomes theo d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Man City c\u1ea7u vi\u1ec7n t\u00e0i n\u0103ng tr\u1ebb tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 t\u1eeb n\u01b0\u1edbc ngo\u00e0i<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"thu mon Bravo\" title=\"thu mon Bravo\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/21/Claudio-Bravo-dinh-chan-thuong-nang-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Claudio Bravo</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">V\u1edbi ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng n\u1eb7ng v\u00e0 nguy c\u01a1 ngh\u1ec9 h\u1ebft m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i c\u1ee7a Claudio Bravo c\u00f9ng vi\u1ec7c Joe Hart \u0111\u00e3 l\u1ea1i ph\u1ea3i ra \u0111i c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Burnley, khung g\u1ed7 s\u00e2n Etihad hi\u1ec7n th\u1eddi kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u00e1n d\u1ef1 ph\u00f2ng h\u1eefu hi\u1ec7u cho th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n s\u1ed1 m\u1ed9t Ederson Moraes. Ch\u00ednh v\u00ec v\u1eady, HLV Pep Guardiola \u0111ang l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch g\u1ecdi tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 t\u00e0i n\u0103ng tr\u1ebb 19 tu\u1ed5i Aro Muric ng\u01b0\u1eddi Montenegro l\u00fac n\u00e0y \u0111ang kho\u00e1c \u00e1o CLB H\u00e0 Lan NAC Breda.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chelsea chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb chia tay ng\u00f4i sao ti\u1ebfp theo<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Drinkwater\" title=\"Drinkwater\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2017/10/26/Diem-tin-bong-da-toi-158-Vi-Man-Utd,-Zidane-san-sang-lat-keo-Juventus-hinh-anh-4.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Danny Drinkwater</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">V\u1edbi s\u1ef1 xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd c\u1ee7a Mateo Kovacic v\u00e0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u1ea7u h\u00e8 l\u00e0 Jorginho, tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa s\u00e2n Stamford Bridge tr\u1edf n\u00ean v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng ch\u1eadt ch\u1ed9i v\u00e0 h\u1ec7 qu\u1ea3 k\u00e9o theo, t\u00e2n HLV Maurizio Sarri s\u1ebd bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch d\u1ecdn d\u1eb9p thanh l\u00fd trong th\u00e1ng cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng c\u1ee7a phi\u00ean ch\u1ee3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng n\u00e0y. Sau khi Tiemoue Bakayoko \u0111\u00e3 ra \u0111i c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn AC Milan, Danny Drinkwater c\u0169ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0 c\u00e1i t\u00ean ti\u1ebfp theo ph\u1ea3i chia tay Chelsea.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sao Tottenham chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb gia nh\u1eadp Paris Saint-Germain<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Danny Rose cua Tottenham\" title=\"Danny Rose cua Tottenham\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/25/Mourinho-len-tieng-vu-MU-mua-Danny-Rose-cua-Tottenham--hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Danny Rose</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">K\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00e8 2018 \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c \u0111\u00f3ng c\u1eeda \u1edf Anh nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ed3ng ngh\u0129a c\u00e1c CLB Premier League kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 quy\u1ec1n b\u00e1n ho\u1eb7c cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. Ch\u00ednh v\u00ec v\u1eady, Danny Rose v\u1eabn c\u00f2n nguy\u00ean c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i c\u1ee9u v\u00e3n s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p v\u1ed1n kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n nhi\u1ec1u ch\u1ed7 \u0111\u1ee9ng \u1edf Spurs. Theo nhi\u1ec1u ngu\u1ed3n tin, h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 tr\u00e1i 28 tu\u1ed5i ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 gia nh\u1eadp \u0111\u1ea1i gia n\u01b0\u1edbc Ph\u00e1p PSG theo d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n trong m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2618","checkdouble":"195016"},{"date":"06:28 22/08","title":"Sir Alex s\u1ebd t\u1ed1ng c\u1ed5 Pogba n\u1ebfu c\u00f2n t\u1ea1i v\u1ecb","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/21/sir-alex-se-tong-co-pogba-neu-con-tai-vi.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>C\u1ef1u danh th\u1ee7 Danny Mills cho bi\u1ebft v\u00ec nhi\u1ec1u l\u00fd do m\u00e0 Jose Mourinho kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ebfn nh\u01b0 ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p \u1edf Old Trafford nh\u01b0 ti\u1ec1n nhi\u1ec7m huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn s\u1ebd l\u00e0m.</h2><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">T\u01b0\u1edfng ch\u1eebng m\u1ed9t th\u00e1ng ch\u00f3i s\u00e1ng tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t Nga c\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Ph\u00e1p l\u00ean ng\u00f4i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup 2018 s\u1ebd gi\u00fap Paul Pogba tho\u1ea3i m\u00e1i tinh th\u1ea7n h\u01a1n khi tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 h\u1ed9i qu\u00e2n \u1edf Old Trafford. Kh\u00f4ng, m\u1ecdi chuy\u1ec7n c\u00f2n tr\u1edf n\u00ean ph\u1ee9c t\u1ea1p mu\u00f4n ph\u1ea7n xoay quanh m\u1ed1i quan h\u1ec7 v\u1edbi Jose Mourinho, k\u00e9o theo \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 c\u1ea3 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a anh trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Qu\u1ef7 \u0110\u1ecf.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Sir Alex Ferguson s\u1ebd t\u1ed1ng c\u1ed5 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Pogba c\u1ee7a MU n\u1ebfu c\u00f2n t\u1ea1i v\u1ecb h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Sir Alex Ferguson s\u1ebd t\u1ed1ng c\u1ed5 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Pogba c\u1ee7a MU n\u1ebfu c\u00f2n t\u1ea1i v\u1ecb h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/21/Cuu-danh-thu-Man-Utd-che-Paul-Pogba-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Sir Alex s\u1ebd t\u1ed1ng c\u1ed5 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Pogba c\u1ee7a MU n\u1ebfu c\u00f2n t\u1ea1i v\u1ecb</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">B\u1ea3n th\u00e2n HLV ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01b0\u1edbng tai gai m\u1eaft l\u1eafm r\u1ed3i v\u1edbi c\u1eadu h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 r\u1eafc r\u1ed1i c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t sau khi ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 25 tu\u1ed5i chia s\u1ebb r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 hi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec7n \u0111i \u1edf c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh: \u201cC\u00f3 nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u m\u00e0 t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ph\u00e9p n\u00f3i ra, b\u1eb1ng kh\u00f4ng s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i ch\u1ecbu s\u1ef1 tr\u1eebng ph\u1ea1t.\u201d M\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t, anh ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c thi \u0111\u1ea5u nh\u1ea1t nh\u00f2a trong tr\u1eadn thua b\u1ea1c nh\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ee7a MU tr\u00ean s\u00e2n Brighton.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 v\u1eady, Mourinho \u0111\u1ee7 \u00fd th\u1ee9c m\u00ecnh \u0111ang \u1edf v\u1ecb th\u1ebf y\u1ebfu h\u01a1n so v\u1edbi Pogba \u1edf Old Trafford v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c g\u00ec nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ec3 \u00edt nh\u1ea5t r\u0103n \u0111e anh. Trong khi \u0111\u00f3, c\u1ef1u danh th\u1ee7 Danny Mills kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh n\u1ebfu Sir Alex Ferguson v\u1eabn c\u00f2n t\u1ea1i v\u1ecb, Pogba hi\u1ec3n nhi\u00ean \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb t\u1ed1ng c\u1ed5 kh\u00f4ng th\u01b0\u01a1ng ti\u1ebfc. Ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u gi\u1ea3i th\u00edch l\u00fd do c\u1ee7a c\u1ef1u h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 t\u1eebng kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Man City v\u00e0 Leeds United:<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u201cPogba \u0111ang g\u00e2y h\u1ea5n v\u1edbi Mourinho c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 c\u1ea3 CLB sau nh\u1eefng g\u00ec chia s\u1ebb tr\u00ean ph\u01b0\u01a1ng ti\u1ec7n truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng x\u00e3 h\u1ed9i? N\u1ebfu Sir Alex c\u00f2n \u1edf \u0111\u00e2y, t\u00f4i ngh\u0129 anh ta \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb t\u1ed1ng c\u1ed5 kh\u00f4ng th\u01b0\u01a1ng ti\u1ebfc kh\u1ecfi Man Utd. V\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 l\u00e0 Pogba hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i qu\u00e1 \u0111\u1ed7i quan tr\u1ecdng v\u1edbi Man Utd, trong khi Mourinho \u0111ang \u1edf th\u1ebf y\u1ebfu \u0111\u1ec3 kh\u00f3 c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng l\u00e0m g\u00ec, th\u1eadm ch\u00ed c\u00f2n ph\u1ea3i lo nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n cho t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a ch\u00ednh m\u00ecnh.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u201cB\u00ean c\u1ea1nh \u0111\u00f3 quan tr\u1ecdng, Sir Alex \u0111\u1ee7 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng v\u00e0 s\u1ef1 t\u1ef1 tin \u0111\u1ec3 thay th\u1ebf m\u1ecdi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 d\u00f9 c\u00f3 l\u00e0 ng\u00f4i sao l\u1edbn t\u1ea7m c\u1ee1 nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf n\u00e0o, nh\u01b0 vi\u1ec7c \u00f4ng gi\u1edbi thi\u1ec7u Rio Ferdinand hay Cristiano Ronaldo ngay sau khi lo\u1ea1i b\u1ecf Jaap Stam v\u00e0 David Beckham. Mourinho \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 l\u00e0m \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 v\u00e0 v\u1eabn \u0111ang ph\u1ea3i d\u1ef1a d\u1eabm v\u00e0o Pogba, chung quy c\u0169ng b\u1edfi \u00f4ng \u1ea5y kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 10-15 kinh nghi\u1ec7m th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng \u1edf CLB \u0111\u1ec3 x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng ti\u1ebfng n\u00f3i v\u00e0 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/du-am-mu-vs-man-city-172-194853.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/20/mourinho-cay-dang-chia-se-ve-tran-thua-tham-o-brighton.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/du-am-mu-vs-man-city-172-194853.html\">Man Utd thua th\u1ea3m: \u0110\u00fang r\u1ed3i Jose, ti\u1ec1n kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 mua \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p!</span><br>\r\nTh\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i b\u1ea1c nh\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u01b0\u1edbc Brighton cho th\u1ea5y Jose Mourinho gi\u1edd \u1edf v\u1ecb th\u1ebf m\u00e0 l\u1eddi m\u1ec9a mai Man City nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf c\u1ee7a \u00f4ng kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00e1ng cho Pep Guardiola ph\u1ea3i ch\u1ea5p n\u1eefa r\u1ed3i,...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/du-am-mu-vs-man-city-172-194855.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/20/Du-am-Brighton-vs-MU-Dung-roi-Jose,-tien-khong-the-mua-dang-cap-hinh-anh.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/du-am-mu-vs-man-city-172-194855.html\">M.U phi\u00ean b\u1ea3n Jose Mourinho: Con thuy\u1ec1n m\u1ea5t ph\u01b0\u01a1ng h\u01b0\u1edbng</span><br>\r\nN\u1ed7i th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng t\u01b0\u1edfng ch\u1eebng nh\u01b0 \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ea1m \u0111\u00e1y c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c C\u0110V Qu\u1ef7 \u0110\u1ecf t\u1ed9i nghi\u1ec7p cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng v\u1eabn b\u1ecb k\u00e9o xu\u1ed1ng s\u00e2u h\u01a1n n\u1eefa sau th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i b\u1ea1c nh\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u01b0\u1edbc Brighton. L\u1eddi...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<strong>Gia Khoa (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2617","checkdouble":"195017"},{"date":"06:56 22/08","title":"Emery b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 t\u1edbi t\u1ea5p sau b\u00e3o ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/8/19/emery-bat-ngo-duoc-bao-ve-toi-tap-sau-bao-chi-trich.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Henrikh Mkhitaryan c\u00f9ng huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i Gary Neville k\u00eau g\u1ecdi gi\u1edbi m\u1ed9 \u0111i\u1ec7u ki\u00ean nh\u1eabn v\u1edbi tri\u1ebft l\u00fd b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 m\u1edbi \u0111ang \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u00e2n HLV ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha \u1edf Arsenal.</h2><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Thua s\u1ea1ch hai tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean \u1edf Premier League 2018/19 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Man City v\u00e0 Chelsea, t\u00e2n HLV Unai Emery \u0111\u00e3 s\u1edbm \u0111\u1eb7t m\u00ecnh trong \u00e1p l\u1ef1c ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch c\u1ee7a d\u01b0 lu\u1eadn, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t v\u1edbi l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng theo tri\u1ebft l\u00fd tri\u1ec3n khai t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng t\u1eeb ph\u1ea7n s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 m\u00e0 theo \u0111\u1ed3ng nghi\u1ec7p Sam Allardyce m\u1ec9a mai l\u00e0 <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/tan-hlv-arsenal-bi-chi-trich-hoc-doi-man-city-172-194568.html\" target=\"_blank\">h\u1ecdc \u0111\u00f2i Manchester City</span>.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u201c\u0110\u00e2y ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n l\u00e0 l\u1ed7i c\u1ee7a HLV, anh \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf tr\u01b0\u1edbc Man City khi g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng ph\u00e1t \u0111\u1ed9ng t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng t\u1eeb ph\u1ea7n s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 y nh\u01b0 h\u1ecd. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t s\u1ef1 b\u1eaft ch\u01b0\u1edbc n\u1eeda v\u1eddi v\u00e0 nghi\u00eam tr\u1ecdng h\u01a1n, n\u00f3 c\u00e0ng khi\u1ebfn Man City d\u1ec5 \u0111\u00e1 v\u1edbi c\u00e1ch pressing c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. Khi n\u00e0o gi\u1ecfi nh\u01b0 Man City r\u1ed3i anh mu\u1ed1n l\u00e0m g\u00ec th\u00ec l\u00e0m.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Mkhitaryan b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 t\u00e2n HLV Emery c\u1ee7a Arsenal b\u1ecb ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Mkhitaryan b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 t\u00e2n HLV Emery c\u1ee7a Arsenal b\u1ecb ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/19/emery-6.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Mkhitaryan b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 t\u00e2n HLV Emery c\u1ee7a Arsenal</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Tuy nhi\u00ean m\u1edbi g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y, phe \u1ee7ng h\u1ed9 Emery m\u1edbi b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng v\u1edbi tr\u01b0\u1edbc h\u1ebft l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi ph\u1ea3n ph\u00e1o quan \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u1ee7a Gary Neville d\u00e0nh cho Big Sam. Ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u c\u1ee7a huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i Man Utd: \u201cTh\u00f4i n\u00e0o, anh \u1ea5y m\u1edbi \u0111\u1ebfn \u0111\u00e2y c\u00f3 5-6 tu\u1ea7n th\u00f4i v\u00e0 c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng d\u1eabn d\u1eaft m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng tr\u00e1nh xu\u1ed1ng h\u1ea1ng.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u201cEmery \u0111ang x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u1ee7 s\u1ee9c c\u1ea1nh tranh ng\u00f4i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh hay \u00edt nh\u1ea5t c\u0169ng ph\u1ea3i top 4, th\u1ebf n\u00ean l\u00e0m sao c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00f2i h\u1ecfi Arsenal ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng d\u00e0i v\u00e0 c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng gi\u00e0nh 8 \u0111i\u1ec3m sau 5 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c. T\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng bi\u1ebft Emery c\u00f3 l\u00e0m \u0111\u00fang v\u00e0 s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c hay kh\u00f4ng, nh\u01b0ng anh \u1ea5y ch\u00ed \u00edt c\u0169ng ngh\u0129 \u0111\u00fang v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t b\u1ea3n s\u1eafc b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng \u0111\u1eb9p m\u1eaft.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Trong khi \u0111\u00f3, Henrikh Mkhitaryan c\u0169ng m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y m\u1edbi c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Armenia ghi b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean cho Arsenal \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y chia s\u1ebb: \u201cM\u1ecdi chuy\u1ec7n ban \u0111\u1ea7u hi\u1ec3n nhi\u00ean kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n b\u1edfi c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 v\u1ed1n ph\u1ea3i c\u00f3 th\u1eddi gian l\u00e0m quen d\u1ea7n d\u00e0 v\u1edbi tri\u1ebft l\u00fd b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 m\u1edbi. Tinh th\u1ea7n chung c\u1ee7a Wenger v\u1eabn c\u00f2n nguy\u00ean nh\u01b0ng Emery mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 c\u00e1i g\u00ec \u0111\u00f3 kh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t h\u01a1n, nh\u01b0 s\u1ef1 c\u00e2n b\u1eb1ng gi\u1eefa c\u00f4ng v\u00e0 th\u1ee7.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u201cCh\u00fang t\u00f4i ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn \u0111ang \u0111i \u0111\u00fang h\u01b0\u1edbng v\u00e0 b\u1ea5t ch\u1ea5p kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n, t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed3ng l\u00f2ng c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng v\u00ec HLV m\u1edbi c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, \u0111i\u1ec3n h\u00ecnh nh\u01b0 l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t th\u1ebf tr\u1eadn ch\u1ee9 kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 c\u1ee9 \u0111\u00e1 qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng l\u00ean ph\u00eda tr\u00ean m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch b\u1ecb \u0111\u1ed9ng. N\u1ebfu \u0111\u1ec3 \u00fd, nh\u1eefng b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang t\u00f4i v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi Chelsea \u0111\u1ec1u l\u00e0 th\u00e0nh qu\u1ea3 k\u1ebft tinh c\u1ee7a kho\u1ea3ng 20 \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ea5y v\u00e0 \u0111\u00f3 ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec3m t\u00edch c\u1ef1c kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/arsenal-thua-tran-thu-hai-lien-tiep-unai-emery-can-them-bao-nhieu-thoi-gian-172-194779.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/18/arsenal-thua-tran-thu-hai-lien-tiep-unai-emery-can-them-bao-nhieu-thoi-gian.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/arsenal-thua-tran-thu-hai-lien-tiep-unai-emery-can-them-bao-nhieu-thoi-gian-172-194779.html\">Arsenal thua tr\u1eadn th\u1ee9 hai li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp: Unai Emery c\u1ea7n th\u00eam bao nhi\u00eau th\u1eddi gian?</span><br>\r\nTh\u00eam nh\u1eefng v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u01b0a ra m\u1ed5 x\u1ebb sau khi Arsenal \u0111\u1ec3 thua Chelsea nh\u01b0ng c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 c\u1ee7a Unai Emery v\u1eabn mang \u0111\u1ebfn nh\u1eefng t\u00edn hi\u1ec7u t\u00edch c\u1ef1c nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ecbnh.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><strong>Gia Khoa (TTVN)</strong><o:p></o:p></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2616","checkdouble":"195018"},{"date":"16:44 21/08","title":"Morata \u0111\u1eb7t ra m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau l\u1edbn t\u1ea1i Chelsea","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/17/morata-dat-ra-muc-tieu-lon-tai-chelsea.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Sau khi m\u1edf t\u00e0i kho\u1ea3n trong m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Alvaro Morata mu\u1ed1n ghi nhi\u1ec1u b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf t\u00e0i n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.\r\n</h2><h2><br>\r\nMorata \u0111\u1eb7t m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau l\u1edbn t\u1ea1i Chelsea<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">B\u1ecb nghi ng\u1edd v\u1ec1 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng \u1edf l\u1ea1i, nh\u01b0ng sau c\u00f9ng ch\u00e2n s\u00fat T\u00e2y Ban Nha v\u1eabn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tin t\u01b0\u1edfng t\u1ea1i Stamford Bridge, sau khi nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ed3ng thu\u1eadn t\u1eeb BL\u0110 v\u00e0 t\u00e2n HLV Maurizio Sarri. M\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, Alvaro Morata c\u0169ng c\u00f3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi, v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 r\u1ea5t m\u1ea1nh l\u00e0 Arsenal.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y cho bi\u1ebft: &ldquo;M\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi t\u00f4i, v\u00e0 \u0111\u00f3 kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 v\u1ec1 ni\u1ec1m tin. T\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 g\u1eb7p ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eefng ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng, v\u00e0 t\u00e2m l\u00fd c\u0169ng b\u1ecb \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng. D\u00f9 v\u1eady, m\u1ecdi th\u1ee9 s\u1ebd tr\u00f4i qua ch\u1ec9 c\u1ea7n t\u00f4i t\u00ecm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u00e0nh l\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng. T\u00f4i \u0111ang r\u1ea5t tho\u1ea3i m\u00e1i v\u00e0 hy v\u1ecdng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u b\u00e0n th\u1eafng.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;T\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean, t\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n ghi tr\u00ean 30 b\u00e0n \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y. Nh\u01b0ng n\u1ebfu \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1ecdn, t\u00f4i th\u00edch ghi 15-20 b\u00e0n v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Premier League h\u01a1n, ho\u1eb7c danh hi\u1ec7u n\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3 l\u1edbn. T\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n l\u1eadp c\u00f4ng nhi\u1ec1u nh\u1ea5t c\u00f3 th\u1ec3, nh\u01b0ng \u0111i\u1ec1u quan tr\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t v\u1eabn l\u00e0 th\u00e0nh t\u00edch c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng.&rdquo;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Alvaro Morata mu\u1ed1n ghi nhi\u1ec1u b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y\" title=\"Morata\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/20/morata-toi-chua-tung-nghi-den-chuyen-roi-chelsea.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Alvaro Morata mu\u1ed1n ghi nhi\u1ec1u b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nChia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 t\u00ecnh h\u00ecnh hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i d\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi HLV m\u1edbi, ch\u00e2n s\u00fat sinh n\u0103m 1992 ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c: &ldquo;\u00d4ng \u1ea5y mu\u1ed1n ch\u00fang t\u00f4i ch\u01a1i t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng v\u00e0 gi\u00e0nh quy\u1ec1n ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t b\u00f3ng. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n t\u1eeb nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u nh\u1ecf nh\u1ea5t, nh\u01b0ng to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i m\u1edbi l\u00e0m quen chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt trong v\u00f2ng 1 th\u00e1ng v\u1eeba qua. Hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 \u0111ang \u1ee7ng h\u1ed9 HLV m\u1edbi, v\u00e0 t\u00f4i ngh\u0129 n\u1ebfu Chelsea ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c theo h\u01b0\u1edbng n\u00e0y, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1edbi b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 CLB n\u00e0o tr\u00ean th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;T\u00f4i r\u1ea5t h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac v\u1edbi 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m quan tr\u1ecdng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Arsenal. T\u1ea1i Premier League, n\u1ebfu b\u1ea1n gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng trong 5 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean, b\u1ea1n s\u1ebd c\u00f3 l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf l\u1edbn. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c duy tr\u00ec phong \u0111\u1ed9 n\u00e0y&rdquo; &ndash; Alvaro Morata mu\u1ed1n ghi nhi\u1ec1u b\u00e0n th\u1eafng v\u00e0 \u0111\u1eb7t m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau l\u1edbn.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/eden-hazard-se-ngay-lap-tuc-roi-chelsea-neu-172-194971.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/19/eden-hazard-se-ngay-lap-tuc-roi-chelsea-neu.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/eden-hazard-se-ngay-lap-tuc-roi-chelsea-neu-172-194971.html\">Eden Hazard s\u1ebd ngay l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c r\u1eddi Chelsea n\u1ebfu...</span><br>\r\nEden Hazard r\u1eddi Chelsea v\u00e0o H\u00e8 2019 n\u1ebfu \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c kh\u00f4ng gi\u00e0nh v\u00e9 d\u1ef1 Champions League, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 th\u00f4ng tin \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1edd The Sun \u0111\u0103ng t\u1ea3i.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/huyen-thoai-chi-ra-ly-do-khien-arsenal-that-bai-truoc-chelsea-172-194932.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/20/huyen-thoai-chi-ra-ly-do-khien-arsenal-that-bai-truoc-chelsea.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/huyen-thoai-chi-ra-ly-do-khien-arsenal-that-bai-truoc-chelsea-172-194932.html\">Huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i ch\u1ec9 ra l\u00fd do khi\u1ebfn Arsenal th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i tr\u01b0\u1edbc Chelsea</span><br>\r\nIan Wright ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Arsenal, ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u0169 c\u1ee7a Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh ch\u00ednh nh\u1eefng sai l\u1ea7m c\u1ee7a Alexandre Lacazette l\u00e0 l\u00fd do khi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London th\u1ea5t th\u1ee7...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2615","checkdouble":"194991"},{"date":"16:32 21/08","title":"Nh\u00ecn l\u1ea1i nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn thua c\u1ee7a b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Bahrain tr\u01b0\u1edbc Vi\u1ec7t Nam","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2016/10/26/Khep-lai-VCK-U19-chau-A-2016-Buoc-ngoat-lich-su-hinh-anh-2.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Trong qu\u00e1 kh\u1ee9, c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng \u00edt l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Bahrain. V\u00e0 t\u1ef7 l\u1ec7 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u0111ang nghi\u00eang h\u1eb3n v\u1ec1 ph\u00eda Vi\u1ec7t Nam.</h2><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111ang \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xem l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 k\u1ecb d\u01a1 c\u1ee7a b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Bahrain b\u1edfi \u1edf 4 l\u1ea7n g\u1eb7p nhau trong qu\u00e1 kh\u1ee9, ch\u00fang ta \u0111\u00e3 th\u1eafng t\u1edbi 3. V\u00e0 h\u00e3y nh\u00ecn l\u1ea1i nh\u1eefng th\u1eafng l\u1ee3i \u0111\u00f3 c\u1ee7a \u0111o\u00e0n qu\u00e2n \u00e1o \u0111\u1ecf.</p>\r\n<h2>1. U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam 1-0 U19 Bahrain (2016)</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng c\u1ea3m x\u00fac nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam tr\u01b0\u1edbc Bahrain ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam v\u00e0 U19 Bahrain t\u1ea1i t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft gi\u1ea3i U19 ch\u00e2u \u00c1 n\u0103m 2016.\u00a0</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Khi \u0111\u00f3 th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Ho\u00e0ng Anh Tu\u1ea5n \u0111\u00e3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng qu\u1ea3 c\u1ea3m \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 Bahrain nh\u1edd b\u00e0n th\u1eafng duy nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ghi b\u1edfi ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Tr\u1ea7n Th\u00e0nh.\u00a0Chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng quan tr\u1ecdng \u1ea5y \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00fap U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh m\u1ed9t trong b\u1ed1n \u0111\u1ed9i c\u1ee7a ch\u00e2u \u00c1 gi\u00e0nh v\u00e9 d\u1ef1 VCK U20 World Cup 2017 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c t\u1ea1i H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c. <br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u00e2y c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 n\u00f3i l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng l\u1ecbch s\u1eed c\u1ee7a b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 n\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u00e0 b\u1edfi \u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean trong l\u1ecbch s\u1eed b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 11 ng\u01b0\u1eddi, Vi\u1ec7t Nam c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t \u1edf \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1eddng th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c bi\u1ebft, l\u00fac n\u00e0y Olympic Bahrain \u0111ang c\u00f3 7 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 t\u1eebng thua U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam c\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y 2 n\u0103m. V\u00e0 r\u1ea5t c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 h\u1ecd s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn th\u00eam m\u1ed9t th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i n\u1eefa tr\u01b0\u1edbc Quang H\u1ea3i, \u0110\u1ee9c Chinh \u1edf l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u t\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y.</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u00ecn l\u1ea1i nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn gi\u1eefa b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs Bahrain h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Nh\u00ecn l\u1ea1i nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn gi\u1eefa b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs Bahrain h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2016/10/26/Khep-lai-VCK-U19-chau-A-2016-Buoc-ngoat-lich-su-hinh-anh-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Quang H\u1ea3i v\u00e0 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i t\u1eebng \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i ng\u01b0\u1eddi Bahrain \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh v\u00e9 d\u1ef1 U20 World Cup</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>2. Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam 3-1 Olympic Bahrain (2010)</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede ASIAD 2010, Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam d\u01b0\u1edbi s\u1ef1 d\u1eabn d\u1eaft c\u1ee7a HLV Phan Thanh H\u00f9ng \u0111\u00e3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00e1 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng. \u1ede b\u1ea3ng B c\u00f9ng Olympic Iran, Turkmenistan v\u00e0 Bahrain, c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 n\u00f3i c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111i ti\u1ebfp l\u00fac \u0111\u00f3 v\u1edbi \u0111o\u00e0n qu\u00e2n \u00e1o \u0111\u1ecf l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng nhi\u1ec1u.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tuy nhi\u00ean ngay \u1edf tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n, th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Phan Thanh H\u00f9ng \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ea1o b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd khi \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 T\u00e2y \u00c1 n\u00e0y v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 3-1 chung cu\u1ed9c.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y, \u0110inh Thanh Trung l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi m\u1edf t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 cho Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u1edf ph\u00fat 34 c\u1ee7a tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u. Tr\u00ean \u0111\u00e0 h\u01b0ng ph\u1ea5n, l\u1ea7n l\u01b0\u1ee3t Tr\u1ecdng Ho\u00e0ng v\u00e0 Anh \u0110\u1ee9c ghi th\u00eam hai b\u00e0n n\u1eefa \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00fap Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam c\u1ea7m ch\u1eafc chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng.\u00a0</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Olympic Viet Nam 2010\" title=\"Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam 2010\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/21/viet-nam-bahrain-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam n\u0103m 2010 c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 h\u1ea1 Bahrain t\u1ea1i ASIAD</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ph\u00eda Bahrain sau nhi\u1ec1u n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 1 b\u00e0n danh d\u1ef1 do Isa ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u00ean ch\u1ea5m ph\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ec1n qua \u0111\u00f3 ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i 1-3 \u1edf ng\u00e0y ra qu\u00e2n ASIAD n\u0103m \u0111\u00f3.\u00a0</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u1eadn Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam 3-1 Olympic Bahrain c\u0169ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 n\u00f3i l\u00e0 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng l\u1ecbch s\u1eed c\u1ee7a b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u1edf ASIAD b\u1edfi nh\u1edd 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m qu\u00fd gi\u00e1 \u1edf tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y, th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Phan Thanh H\u00f9ng m\u1edbi c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng ASIAD, \u0111i\u1ec1u m\u00e0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3 ch\u00fang ta ch\u01b0a t\u1eebng th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c.</p>\r\n<h2>3. \u0110T Vi\u1ec7t Nam 5-3 Bahrain (2007)</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m VCK Asian Cup 2007, b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ed9 Bahrain \u1edf c\u1ea5p \u0111\u1ed9 \u0110TQG. Tuy nhi\u00ean \u0111\u00f3 ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 \u1edf m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u giao h\u1eefu. V\u00e0 r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng \u1edf m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00f4 th\u01b0\u1edfng, v\u00f4 ph\u1ea1t, hai b\u00ean \u0111\u00e3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00e1 c\u1edfi m\u1edf v\u00e0 c\u1ed1ng hi\u1ebfn t\u1edbi 8 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng cho NHM.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Abdulrahman l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi m\u1edf t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u ngay \u1edf ph\u00fat th\u1ee9 3 sau sai l\u1ea7m c\u1ee7a th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n D\u01b0\u01a1ng H\u1ed3ng S\u01a1n. Tuy nhi\u00ean sau \u0111\u00f3, V\u0103n Nhi\u00ean, C\u00f4ng Vinh v\u00e0 Ti\u1ebfn Th\u00e0nh l\u1ea7n l\u01b0\u1ee3t mang v\u1ec1 nh\u1eefng b\u00e0n th\u1eafng cho \u0110T Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u1edf c\u00e1c ph\u00fat 11, 16 v\u00e0 52 \u0111\u1ec3 th\u1eafng ng\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ea1i 3-1.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sang hi\u1ec7p 2, s\u1ef1 l\u01a1 l\u00e0 c\u1ee7a h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 \u0110T Vi\u1ec7t Nam gi\u00fap Bahrain c\u00f3 hai b\u00e0n g\u1ee1, tuy nhi\u00ean \u1edf nh\u1eefng ph\u00fat cu\u1ed1i, \u0110T Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u00e3 gia t\u0103ng s\u1ee9c \u00e9p v\u00e0 c\u00f3 th\u00eam hai b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a Thanh B\u00ecnh v\u00e0 Anh \u0110\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh th\u1eafng l\u1ee3i chung cu\u1ed9c 5-3.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-han-quoc-hoi-han-vi-de-thua-malaysia-168-194980.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/17/hlv-han-quoc-hoi-han-vi-de-thua-malaysia.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-han-quoc-hoi-han-vi-de-thua-malaysia-168-194980.html\">HLV H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c v\u1eabn \u00e2n h\u1eadn v\u00ec \u0111\u1ec3 thua Malaysia</span><br>\r\nVi\u1ec7c xem th\u01b0\u1eddng s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh \u0110T Malaysia c\u1ee7a BHL \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c v\u00f4 t\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ea9y h\u1ecd v\u00e0o th\u1ebf kh\u00f3 khi ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ed1i m\u1eb7t v\u1edbi nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 m\u1ea1nh \u1edf ASIAD.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/chinh-thuc-da-co-ban-quyen-asiad-tai-viet-nam-168-194974.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/19/chinh-thuc-da-co-ban-quyen-asiad-tai-viet-nam.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/chinh-thuc-da-co-ban-quyen-asiad-tai-viet-nam-168-194974.html\">CH\u00cdNH TH\u1ee8C: \u0110\u00e3 c\u00f3 b\u1ea3n quy\u1ec1n ASIAD t\u1ea1i Vi\u1ec7t Nam</span><br>\r\nTrang ch\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a \u0110\u00e0i ti\u1ebfng n\u00f3i Vi\u1ec7t Nam VOV \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn s\u1edf h\u1eefu b\u1ea3n quy\u1ec1n ph\u00e1t s\u00f3ng ASIAD 2018 tr\u00ean to\u00e0n b\u1ed9 l\u00e3nh th\u1ed5 Vi\u1ec7t Nam.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-bahrain-noi-dieu-bat-ngo-ve-dt-olympic-viet-nam-168-194953.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/21/hlv-bahrain-noi-dieu-bat-ngo-ve-dt-olympic-viet-nam.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-bahrain-noi-dieu-bat-ngo-ve-dt-olympic-viet-nam-168-194953.html\">HLV Bahrain n\u00f3i \u0111i\u1ec1u b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd v\u1ec1 \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam</span><br>\r\nChia s\u1ebb sau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng quan tr\u1ecdng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Malaysia, HLV tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0110T Olympic Bahrain \u00f4ng Samir Chammam cho bi\u1ebft m\u00ecnh ch\u01b0a t\u00ecm hi\u1ec3u g\u00ec v\u1ec1 \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)</p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2614","checkdouble":"194992"},{"date":"17:18 21/08","title":"Barca ch\u1ed1t gi\u00e1 mua sao tr\u1ebb Ph\u00e1p","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2017/10/8/barca-chot-gia-mua-adrien-rabiot.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Aaron Ramsey r\u1eddi Arsenal t\u0103ng l\u00ean \u0111\u00e1ng k\u1ec3, t\u1edd Daily Mail kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi x\u1ee9 Wales \u0111ang r\u1ea5t t\u1ee9c gi\u1eadn khi ph\u1ea3i ng\u1ed3i d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb \u1edf tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Chelsea.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ramsey t\u1ee9c gi\u1eadn v\u00ec ph\u1ea3i ng\u1ed3i d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nT\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng 2 Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh 2018/19 Arsenal c\u00f3 chuy\u1ebfn l\u00e0m kh\u00e1ch tr\u00ean s\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Chelsea, Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c tr\u00ean s\u00e2n Stamford Bridge nh\u01b0ng v\u1eabn ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 2-3.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"M\u00e2u thu\u1eabn v\u1edbi HLV Emery, Aaron Ramsey r\u1eddi Arsenal \u1edf H\u00e8 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"M\u00e2u thu\u1eabn v\u1edbi HLV Emery, Aaron Ramsey r\u1eddi Arsenal \u1edf H\u00e8 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/21/ramsey-choang-vang-voi-quyet-dinh-cua-hlv-unai-emery.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Ramsey kh\u00f4ng h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c ng\u1ed3i d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb \u1edf tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Chelsea</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u1ede tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Chelsea HLV Unai Emery s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng s\u01a1 \u0111\u1ed3 4-2-3-1 v\u1edbi Guendouzi v\u00e0 Xhaka \u0111\u00e1 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trung t\u00e2m, Mesut Ozil ch\u01a1i trong vai tr\u00f2 c\u1ee7a m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 10. Aaron Ramsey b\u1ecb b\u1ecf r\u01a1i tr\u00ean b\u0103ng gh\u1ebf d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 28 tu\u1ed5i ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u00e0o s\u00e2n \u1edf ph\u00fat 67 thay Ozil.\u00a0</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nKh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Aaron Ramsey r\u1eddi Arsenal t\u0103ng l\u00ean \u0111\u00e1ng k\u1ec3, t\u1edd Daily Mail kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi x\u1ee9 Wales \u0111ang r\u1ea5t t\u1ee9c gi\u1eadn khi ph\u1ea3i ng\u1ed3i d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb \u1edf tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Chelsea.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nRamsey kh\u00f4ng h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng khi ph\u1ea3i ng\u1ed3i d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb, anh mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u1eb7n h\u00e0ng tu\u1ea7n. D\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi HLV Wenger c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1990 l\u00e0 nh\u00e2n t\u1ed1 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 thay th\u1ebf \u1edf tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa, b\u1edfi v\u1eady vi\u1ec7c b\u1ecb HLV Emery lo\u1ea1i kh\u1ecfi k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch khi\u1ebfn anh r\u1ea5t t\u1ee9c gi\u1eadn.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Ramsey r\u1eddi Arsenal t\u0103ng l\u00ean r\u00f5 r\u1ec7t</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh tr\u01b0\u1edbc Chelsea, Ramsey \u0111ang c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y kh\u00f4ng h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac d\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi HLV Unai Emery. Kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng anh r\u1eddi s\u00e2n Emirates \u0111ang l\u00ean l\u00ean \u0111\u00e1ng k\u1ec3.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Aaron Ramsey\" title=\"Aaron Ramsey\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/20/arsenal-nhan-tin-cuc-buon-tu-aaron-ramsey.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Aaron Ramsey ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n 1 n\u0103m h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Arsenal</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nH\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u1ee7a Ramsey v\u1edbi Arsenal ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n th\u1eddi h\u1ea1n 1 n\u0103m, Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7 \u0111ang n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi x\u1ee9 Wales gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi.\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTuy nhi\u00ean, vi\u1ec7c kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Emery tr\u1ecdng d\u1ee5ng v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng m\u1ee9c l\u01b0\u01a1ng nh\u01b0 mong mu\u1ed1n khi\u1ebfn kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Ramsey t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi v\u00e0 ra \u0111i l\u00e0 ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 x\u1ea3y ra.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/chelsea-muon-mua-ramsey-va-vecino-172-192315.html\" target=\"_blank\">Chelsea s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng mua Ramsey</span> v\u00e0o th\u00e1ng 1 n\u0103m 2019, hai \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Manchester c\u0169ng s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng chi 30 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 28 tu\u1ed5i.\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u00e0o th\u00e1ng 1 n\u0103m 2018, Arsenal \u0111\u00e3 bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ec3 Sanchez t\u1edbi M.U, kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Ramsey r\u1eddi Emirates v\u00e0o th\u00e1ng 1 n\u0103m 2019 l\u00e0 ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 x\u1ea3y ra.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2613","checkdouble":"194994"},{"date":"17:45 21/08","title":"B\u1ea1n c\u0169 C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng s\u1eafp r\u1eddi Man City","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/21/jason-denayer-sap-roi-man-city.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Jason Denayer s\u1eafp r\u1eddi Man City. H\u1eadu v\u1ec7 t\u1eebng \u0103n t\u1eadp c\u00f9ng C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Lyon h\u1ecfi mua v\u1edbi m\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 10 tri\u1ec7u Euro v\u00e0 \u0111\u00e3 nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 ch\u1ea5p thu\u1eadn t\u1eeb CLB ch\u1ee7 qu\u1ea3n.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Denayer kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 ch\u1ed7 \u0111\u1ee9ng \u1edf Man City</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nJason Denayer t\u1eebng c\u00f3 5 n\u0103m \u0111\u00e0o t\u1ea1o \u1edf l\u00f2 JMG n\u01b0\u1edbc B\u1ec9. Trong kho\u1ea3ng th\u1eddi gian \u0111\u00f3, h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 n\u00e0y t\u1eebng t\u1edbi trung t\u00e2m Trung t\u00e2m th\u1ec3 thao H\u00e0m R\u1ed3ng (Gia Lai) \u0103n t\u1eadp c\u00f9ng v\u1edbi l\u1ee9a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb HAGL bao g\u1ed3m c\u1ea3 C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 l\u00fd do h\u1ecd tay b\u1eaft m\u1eb7t m\u1eebng, \u0111\u1ed5i \u00e1o \u0111\u1ea5u sau tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu gi\u1eefa Man City v\u00e0 \u0110T Vi\u1ec7t Nam m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u0103m 2015.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nN\u0103m 2013, Denayer chuy\u1ec3n \u0111\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u1ebb Man City. T\u1eeb \u0111\u00f3 t\u1edbi nay, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 \u0111\u00e3 g\u00e2y \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u1edf c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u1ebb CLB v\u00e0 c\u1ea3 khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n t\u1ea1i Celtic, Galatasaray hay Sunderland. Tuy nhi\u00ean, anh kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o ra d\u1ea5u \u1ea5n trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh to\u00e0n sao c\u1ee7a Pep Guardiola.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Jason Denayer s\u1eafp r\u1eddi Man City \u0111\u1ebfn Lyon h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Jason Denayer s\u1eafp r\u1eddi Man City \u0111\u1ebfn Lyon h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/21/jason-denayer-sap-roi-man-city.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Jason Denayer s\u1eafp r\u1eddi Man City</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>S\u1eafp l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u1ee7a Lyon</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nDenayer kh\u00f4ng gi\u1ea5u \u00fd \u0111\u1ecbnh r\u1eddi Man City v\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0111\u1ebfn \u01b0a th\u00edch l\u00e0 Lyon c\u1ee7a Ph\u00e1p. Tuy nhi\u00ean, ban \u0111\u1ea7u The Citizens kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n b\u00e1n \u0111\u1ee9t anh. H\u1ecd mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u1ea9y h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 n\u00e0y sang ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u201canh em\u201d c\u00f9ng t\u1eadp \u0111o\u00e0n City Football Group l\u00e0 Girona d\u01b0\u1edbi d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nTuy nhi\u00ean, theo nh\u1eefng th\u00f4ng tin m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t, Jason Denayer s\u1eafp r\u1eddi Man City \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1edbi Lyon. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Ph\u00e1p ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n 10 tri\u1ec7u Euro (9 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng) v\u00e0 r\u1ed1t cu\u1ed9c c\u0169ng nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ed3ng t\u00ecnh t\u1eeb Man City. Th\u00f4ng qua Twitter, Man City c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 th\u00f4ng tin n\u00e0y: \u201cCh\u00fac may m\u1eafn, Jason Denayer, ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00e3 k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng d\u00e0i h\u1ea1n v\u1edbi Lyon.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\nSau khi ho\u00e0n t\u1ea5t nh\u1eefng th\u1ee7 t\u1ee5c cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng bao g\u1ed3m ki\u1ec3m tra y t\u1ebf, Denayer s\u1ebd ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u1ee7a Lyon. M\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc, \u201cS\u01b0 t\u1eed s\u00f4ng Rhone\u201d c\u00e1n \u0111\u00edch Ligue 1 \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed th\u1ee9 3 ch\u1ec9 sau Paris Saint-Germain v\u00e0 Monaco.<br>\r\n<strong><br>\r\nXem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Man City tr\u00ean trang bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/man-city-len-ke-hoach-gia-han-hop-dong-voi-john-stones-172-194898.html\">Man City l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch tr\u00f3i ch\u00e2n tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/man-city-chi-60-trieu-bang-mua-ruben-neves-vao-thang-1-172-194884.html\">Man City chi 60 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua Ruben Neves v\u00e0o th\u00e1ng 1</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/patrick-roberts-sap-roi-man-city-sang-girona-172-194473.html\">Th\u00eam m\u1ed9t sao tr\u1ebb chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb r\u1eddi Man City</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/sterling-toa-sang-tro-lai-guardiola-cau-khan-gia-han-voi-man-city-172-194465.html\">Sterling t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i, Guardiola c\u1ea7u kh\u1ea9n gia h\u1ea1n v\u1edbi Man City</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/pep-co-vai-dieu-muon-gui-den-man-city-va-sterling-172-194403.html\">Pep c\u00f3 v\u00e0i \u0111i\u1ec1u mu\u1ed1n g\u1eedi \u0111\u1ebfn Man City v\u00e0 Sterling</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/pep-guardiola-man-city-het-tien-mua-cau-thu-roi-172-194212.html\">Pep Guardiola: \u201cMan City h\u1ebft ti\u1ec1n mua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 r\u1ed3i!\u201d</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nGia Vi (TTVN)<br>\r\n</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2612","checkdouble":"194995"},{"date":"17:13 21/08","title":"MU ph\u1ea3n \u1ee9ng ra sao tr\u01b0\u1edbc tin \u0111\u1ed3n sa th\u1ea3i Mourinho b\u1ed5 nhi\u1ec7m Zidane?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/21/mu-phan-ung-ra-sao-sau-tin-don-sa-thai-mourinho-bo-nhiem-zidane.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>MU sa th\u1ea3i Jose Mourinho b\u1ed5 nhi\u1ec7m Zinedine Zidane l\u00e0 tin \u0111\u1ed3n kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00fang s\u1ef1 th\u1ef1c, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 th\u00f4ng tin \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1edd BBC c\u1ee7a n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh \u0111\u0103ng t\u1ea3i.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">M.U \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ed3n \u0111o\u00e1n nh\u1eafm Zidane thay Mourinho</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nMourinho \u0111ang g\u1eb7p r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u \u00e1p l\u1ef1c \u1edf th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i. Tr\u1eadn thua 2-3 tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u01b0\u1edbc Brighton \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ed9c l\u1ed9 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 c\u1ee7a M.U. \u0110\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Old Trafford kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng, h\u1ecd g\u1eb7p v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 \u1edf c\u1ea3 3 tuy\u1ebfn.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"MU sa th\u1ea3i Jose Mourinho b\u1ed5 nhi\u1ec7m Zinedine Zidane  h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"MU sa th\u1ea3i Jose Mourinho b\u1ed5 nhi\u1ec7m Zinedine Zidane  h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/15/MU-sa-thai-Jose-Mourinho-bo-nhiem-Zinedine-Zidane--hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>M.U \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ed3n \u0111o\u00e1n nh\u1eafm Zidane thay Mourinho</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u1edbi nh\u1eefng g\u00ec \u0111ang th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng M.U v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh m\u00f9a n\u00e0y \u0111ang r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n, th\u1eadm ch\u00ed v\u00e0o Top 4 c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng. V\u1edbi nh\u1eefng g\u00ec \u0111ang di\u1ec5n ra, kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng M.U sa th\u1ea3i Mourinho trong t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai g\u1ea7n l\u00e0 ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTheo Mirror, M.U nh\u1eafm Zinedine Zidane trong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p sa th\u1ea3i Mourinho. \u00d4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p \u0111ang ngh\u1ec9 ng\u01a1i sau th\u1eddi gian d\u1eabn d\u1eaft Real Madrid.\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM.U ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn tr\u1ea3 l\u01b0\u01a1ng r\u1ea5t cao \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi chi m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n l\u1edbn \u0111\u1ec3 Zidane n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh, h\u1ecd \u0111ang r\u1ea5t hy v\u1ecdng l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb n\u00e0y s\u1ebd thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p t\u1edbi Old Trafford.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>M.U ph\u1ee7 nh\u1eadn sa th\u1ea3i Mourinho b\u1ed5 nhi\u1ec7m Zidane</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">MU sa th\u1ea3i Jose Mourinho b\u1ed5 nhi\u1ec7m Zinedine Zidane l\u00e0 tin \u0111\u1ed3n kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00fang s\u1ef1 th\u1ef1c, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 th\u00f4ng tin \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1edd BBC c\u1ee7a n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh \u0111\u0103ng t\u1ea3i.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"MU ph\u1ea3n \u1ee9ng ra sao tr\u01b0\u1edbc tin \u0111\u1ed3n sa th\u1ea3i Mourinho b\u1ed5 nhi\u1ec7m Zidane h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" title=\"MU ph\u1ea3n \u1ee9ng ra sao tr\u01b0\u1edbc tin \u0111\u1ed3n sa th\u1ea3i Mourinho b\u1ed5 nhi\u1ec7m Zidane h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/21/mu-phan-ung-ra-sao-sau-tin-don-sa-thai-mourinho-bo-nhiem-zidane.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>M.U ph\u1ee7 nh\u1eadn vi\u1ec7c sa th\u1ea3i Mourinho b\u1ed5 nhi\u1ec7m Zidane</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u1ed9t ngu\u1ed3n tin t\u1eeb M.U n\u00f3i v\u1edbi t\u1edd BBC: \u201cT\u1ea1i sao ch\u00fang ta l\u1ea1i n\u00f3i \u0111\u1ebfn Zidane khi Mourinho v\u1eabn \u0111ang \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tin t\u01b0\u1edfng tuy\u1ec7t \u0111\u1ed1i, kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 c\u00f3 chuy\u1ec7n ch\u00fang t\u00f4i l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 Zidane thay Mourinho. BL\u0110 v\u1eabn \u0111\u1eb7t ni\u1ec1m tin v\u00e0o Mourinho\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTheo nhi\u1ec1u ngu\u1ed3n tin gi\u1eefa Mourinho v\u00e0 BL\u0110 M.U \u0111ang xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u m\u00e2u thu\u1eabn, \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 \u0111ang c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y kh\u00f4ng h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng khi kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ea5p \u0111\u1ee7 ng\u00e2n s\u00e1ch \u0111\u1ec3 mua s\u1eafm \u1edf k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng H\u00e8 2018.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/mourinho-va-bld-mu-mau-thuan-vi-anthony-martial-172-194990.html\" target=\"_blank\">Mourinho v\u00e0 BL\u0110 M.U c\u0169ng m\u00e2u thu\u1eabn v\u1ec1 Martial</span>. \u00d4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 mu\u1ed1n MU b\u00e1n Anthony Martial ngay \u1edf H\u00e8 2018, song BL\u0110 Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf l\u1ea1i mu\u1ed1n gi\u1eef ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p \u1edf l\u1ea1i Old Trafford.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nL\u00ea H\u01b0\u1eddng (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2611","checkdouble":"194996"}]}